source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000010_YSHTOLA<tab>Your business with Tataru is finished?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000010_YSHTOLA<tab>Alors, qu'est-ce que Tataru te voulait<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000020_YSHTOLA<tab>My, what a thoughtful surprise. Whatever would we do without her?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000020_YSHTOLA<tab>C'est si gentil de sa part. Que ferait-on sans elle, franchement<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000030_THANCRED<tab>Indeed. And she's right, you know─it hasn't been all doom and gloom.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000030_THANCRED<tab>On a connu le meilleur comme le pire, mais Tataru nous prouve une fois de plus qu'on peut tirer parti de nos tribulations.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000040_YSHTOLA<tab>It feels like a lifetime ago that Master Louisoix gathered us together to form the Circle of Knowing.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000040_YSHTOLA<tab>On en a vécu, des aventures. Notre rencontre avec Louisoix, nos débuts au sein du Cénacle du Savoir, le septième fléau, la formation des Héritiers de la Septième Aube...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000050_YSHTOLA<tab>Since then, we have experienced much. But rather than feeling wiser, the more I learn, the more I find my knowledge lacking.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000050_YSHTOLA<tab>Seulement, j'ai l'impression que chaque réponse à nos questions n'a servi qu'à soulever plus de mystères.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000060_URIANGER<tab>Forsooth. As a student, vainly did I believe that I held the secrets of creation in my grasp. Yet that which I had seized was but an insignificant sliver of what awaited in the wider world.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000060_URIANGER<tab>À qui le dites-vous... Jeune étudiant, j'ai eu l'audace de croire que le savoir de Sharlayan était presque absolu. Alors qu'en fait, ce n'était qu'une goutte d'eau perdue dans l'océan de la con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>san<var 16 /var>ce.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000070_URIANGER<tab>Every encounter, every experience, hath served to open mine eyes, enlightening and humbling me in equal measure. Even from those whom I called enemies have I learned many a valuable lesson.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000070_URIANGER<tab>Je l'ai réalisé un peu plus à chaque nouvelle rencontre, à chaque nouvelle découverte. Même mes ennemis ont participé à faire tomber un peu plus mes œillères, et pour ça, je les remercie.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000080_YSHTOLA<tab>What will we learn at the edge of the universe, I wonder...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000080_YSHTOLA<tab>Et voilà qu'on s'apprête à plonger à pieds joints dans un océan d'étoiles. Je me demande bien ce qui nous y attend...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000090_THANCRED<tab>Ultima Thule, where the bringer of the end makes her nest... I for one can't possibly imagine.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000090_THANCRED<tab>Ultima Thulé, là où la chantre de l'ané<var 16 /var>an<var 16 /var>tis<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment a fait son nid... Je sais pas pour vous, mais je suis bien incapable de m'imaginer un endroit pareil...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000100_THANCRED<tab>But whatever awaits us there, we will survive. We <var 1A 02 /var>must<var 1A 01 /var>... For her.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000100_THANCRED<tab>En tout cas, il ne vous arrivera rien. Je l'ai promis à Minfilia.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q1_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q1_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que dites-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A1_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>You've nothing left to prove. Not to Ryne. Nor Minfilia.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A1_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>On compte sur toi, Thancred.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A1_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>We'll get through this. Together.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A1_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Je peux te faire la même promesse.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A1_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>Just make sure you bring enough ammunition.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A1_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>Fais juste attention à ne pas tomber à court de cartouches.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000110_THANCRED<tab>...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000110_THANCRED<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000120_URIANGER<tab>Is aught the matter?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000120_URIANGER<tab>Un problème<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000130_THANCRED<tab>No, it's nothing. I just... Well, lately I find myself surprised at how much I've changed. How much we've all changed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000130_THANCRED<tab>C'est rien... Sur le coup, ça m'a fait réaliser à quel point on a tous bien changé. On n'hésite plus à se parler avec franchise, et à admettre qu'on tient les uns aux autres.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000140_THANCRED<tab> Haha
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000140_THANCRED<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000150_THANCRED<tab>Gods, it feels like only yesterday that we went on that mission to Drybone.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000150_THANCRED<tab>Je sais pas pourquoi, ça me fait penser à cette fois où on est allés tous les deux au camp des Os desséchés. Tu te souviens<var 1D /var>? Tu venais à peine de rejoindre les Héritiers.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000160_THANCRED<tab>We've both changed much since then, have we not?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000160_THANCRED<tab>On a tous les deux bien changé, depuis.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000170_THANCRED<tab>O ye of little faith. I know better than to leave home without ample supplies, thank you very much─I didn't pick up the gunblade yesterday.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000170_THANCRED<tab> La confiance règne<var 1D /var>! T'en fais pas, je fais dans la parcimonie maintenant. J'en garde toujours une sous le coude en cas de besoin.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000180_THANCRED<tab>And to think I used to prefer fighting from the shadows. Gods, I really have changed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000180_THANCRED<tab> Et dire que je faisais dans la furtivité avant. Moi aussi, j'ai bien changé.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000185_YSHTOLA<tab>[AMUSED LAUGH] Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000185_YSHTOLA<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000190_YSHTOLA<tab>We've come far together, and if we have aught to say about it, we'll go further still. Aye, we will avert this calamity and return home.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000190_YSHTOLA<tab>Voilà qui témoigne du chemin parcouru. Je suis certaine que la fin de notre voyage n'est pas encore en vue, pas plus que celle de notre monde.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000200_YSHTOLA<tab>In preparation for which, we must give thought to what we hope to achieve after the proverbial dust has settled.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000200_YSHTOLA<tab>Lorsque l'on sera de retour chez nous, il sera peut-être temps de se poser et de réfléchir à l'avenir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000210_THANCRED<tab>What with the primals and Ascians all but dealt with, I suppose we'll need to look for new hobbies.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000210_THANCRED<tab>Maintenant que tu le dis. La menace des Primordiaux a presque disparu, et celle des Asciens m'a l'air réglée aussi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000220_THANCRED<tab>In all seriousness, though─in uniting to overcome a common foe, the disparate peoples of the world have found a way forward together. It's a truly gratifying sight to see.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000220_THANCRED<tab>Reste à voir si les gens vont voir au-delà de leurs différences et commencer à vivre un peu plus en harmonie. Mais même ça, ça me semble plutôt bien parti.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000230_YSHTOLA<tab>Indeed... Though it was many years in the making, we have successfully set in motion the gears of fundamental change.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000230_YSHTOLA<tab>Oui, c'est vrai. Les problèmes que les Héritiers avaient pris à bras-le-corps semblent tous en bonne voie de se résoudre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000240_YSHTOLA<tab>With this, we have fulfilled our humble role as a symbol of hope...and I daresay it is time to bow out.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000240_YSHTOLA<tab>Il est peut-être temps pour nous de laisser d'autres reprendre le flambeau de l'espoir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000250_YSHTOLA<tab>After all, there is no shortage of hands to bear the torch in our stead.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000250_YSHTOLA<tab>Ce ne sont pas les candidats qui manquent.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000260_THANCRED<tab>You know, I never really considered I might live long enough to see an after.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000260_THANCRED<tab>Ça m'était même pas venu à l'esprit, mais c'est vrai...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000270_THANCRED<tab>But even if my time as a Scion came to an end, I don't expect that much would change.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000270_THANCRED<tab>Que je sois en mission pour les Héritiers ou à mon compte, je doute que mon quotidien change énormément.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000280_THANCRED<tab>Traveling the world, going wherever the wind blows, lending a hand to those in need...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000280_THANCRED<tab>Je voyagerais toujours autant, et j'apporterais mon aide à ceux qui en ont besoin. C'est aussi simple que ça.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000290_URIANGER<tab>A journey for journey's sake. It doth suit thee well. I must confess, I too have yearned to see more of the world.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000290_URIANGER<tab>Cette perspective me plaît. J'ai toujours aspiré à observer l'avenir se tisser sous mes yeux, et j'aimerais continuer à le faire de par le monde.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000300_URIANGER<tab>If thou art amenable to the suggestion, I would accompany thee. Mine ability to affect an air of normalcy through artful disguise is much improved, thou must concede...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000300_URIANGER<tab>Je souhaiterais vous accompagner, si vous le voulez bien. Je puis même me déguiser si la situation demande de faire profil bas.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000310_THANCRED<tab>Aye, well, improvement is relative. You still look suspicious no matter what you wear.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000310_THANCRED<tab>L'ennui, c'est que tu es tout sauf bas de profil. Mais si tu acceptes enfin de me tutoyer, j'y réfléchirai.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000320_THANCRED<tab>What of you, Y'shtola? Any grand plans?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000320_THANCRED<tab>Et toi, Y'shtola<var 1D /var>? Des projets<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000330_YSHTOLA<tab>Why, continue my quest for knowledge, naturally. To begin with, I wish to know the state of the reflections, to which end I must find a means to travel between worlds.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000330_YSHTOLA<tab>Oh, tu me connais. Moi aussi, j'irai de-ci de-là pour trouver la clef de quelque mystère. Je pourrais commencer par chercher un moyen de rejoindre les reflets et étudier l'influence de la disparition d'Hydaelyn.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000340_YSHTOLA<tab>'Tis the least I must do if I am to keep my promise.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000340_YSHTOLA<tab>Après tout, j'ai promis à un grand enfant de répondre à son appel, s'il avait besoin de moi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000350_YSHTOLA<tab>Should my pursuits prove unduly arduous, I won't hesitate to call on you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000350_YSHTOLA<tab>Et si un grave danger m'attend là-bas, j'engagerai votre fine équipe pour surveiller mes arrières.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000360_YSHTOLA<tab>And in return, I will take you to see Ryne one day. I'm sure you cannot wait to see the fine young woman she has become.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000360_YSHTOLA<tab>Ryne aura sûrement bien grandi d'ici là.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000370_THANCRED<tab>Spare me...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000370_THANCRED<tab>Ha... Arrête un peu, s'il te plaît.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000380_URIANGER<tab>And what of thee? What wouldst thou pursue at duty's end?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000380_URIANGER<tab>Et vous<var 1D /var>? Que comptez-vous faire lorsque les Héritiers auront accompli leur tâche<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000390_WAITEROFTHELASTSTAND<tab>Here's yours. My apologies for the wait.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000390_WAITEROFTHELASTSTAND<tab>Et voilà pour vous. Désolé de vous avoir fait attendre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000400_THANCRED<tab>Well, shall we make a toast?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000400_THANCRED<tab>Ça m'a l'air d'être le moment de trinquer.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000410_THANCRED<tab>To victory.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000410_THANCRED<tab>À notre victoire.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000420_URIANGER<tab>To our comrades.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000420_URIANGER<tab>À tous nos compagnons, anciens comme nouveaux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000430_YSHTOLA<tab>To the future of the star.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000430_YSHTOLA<tab>Et à l'avenir de notre monde. Qu'il soit long et prospère.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000440_KRILE<tab>Oh?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000440_KRILE<tab>Tiens<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000450_KRILE<tab> [LAUGH] Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000450_KRILE<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000460_KRILE<tab>Knowing them, they're probably dreaming about the celestial adventures to come.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000460_KRILE<tab>Tu les aurais vus tout à l'heure, prêts à dévorer page après page à la recherche de sorts utiles ou de détails sur l'espace. C'est du joli, tout ça.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000470_KRILE<tab>Just as well. They've been running themselves ragged of late.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000470_KRILE<tab>Pas étonnant, cela dit. Ils n'ont pas arrêté les va-et-vient récemment.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000480_KRILE<tab>Unlike you and the others, I'm a few steps removed from the danger and excitement. The things you all get up to never fail to impress me. But by the same token, I can't help but worry.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000480_KRILE<tab>Ils font tout pour se hisser à ta hauteur, et je les observe de bien plus bas encore, mais j'aime les voir se démener comme ça... J'envie leur enthousiasme, même si parfois ils en font trop à mon goût.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000490_KRILE<tab>Not only for your safety, but...but for your happiness. After everything you've sacrificed, you earned it a thousand times over.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000490_KRILE<tab>Mon rêve... C'est peut-être beaucoup demander... Ce serait que nous parvenions à sauver notre planète, bien sûr, mais aussi que vous y viviez tous heureux ensuite.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000500_KRILE<tab>From the simple pleasures of tucking into a hearty meal or...or collapsing into a comfortable bed...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000500_KRILE<tab>Vous voir plus souvent rire que pleurer, vous regarder vous goinfrer de bons petits plats, ou faire tran<var 16 /var>quil<var 16 /var>le<var 16 /var>ment la sieste comme maintenant...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000510_KRILE<tab>To the grand triumphs of visiting legendary lands or finding true love─you deserve all the joy in the world.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000510_KRILE<tab>Que vos cœurs battent au rythme de vos aventures en découvrant de nouvelles contrées, et au contraire, qu'ils se relaxent en franchissant des seuils familiers.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000520_KRILE<tab>There is so much that life has to offer. So much to be treasured and shared with those we hold dear.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000520_KRILE<tab>Et que vous fassiez tout ça avec des amis chers, évidemment, au moins de temps à autre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000530_KRILE<tab>So promise me this: come what may, you won't give up on your own happiness.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000530_KRILE<tab>Promets-moi. Quelles que soient les difficultés que tu ren<var 16 /var>con<var 16 /var>tre<var 16 /var>ras, ne sacrifie pas un avenir plein de joie pour remporter ton combat.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000540_KRILE<tab>When you're out there, fighting tooth and nail, it's all too easy to forget.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000540_KRILE<tab>Je te dis ça, car c'est la première chose que héros et héroïnes ont tendance à mettre au second plan lorsqu'ils se retrouvent face à un obstacle insurmontable.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000550_KRILE<tab>But in the end, your passions will be your greatest strength of all. Remember that.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000550_KRILE<tab>Je veux que tu le graves en lettres d'or dans ton cœur. Le bonheur est la plus grande source de force, alors ne l'abandonne pas.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000560_GRAHATIA<tab> [GRUMBLE] Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000560_GRAHATIA<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000570_GRAHATIA<tab>Hm... This feels...familiar...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000570_GRAHATIA<tab>Hmm<var 1D /var>? C'est... c'est toi...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000580_GRAHATIA<tab>Well, 'tis good to be...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000580_GRAHATIA<tab> Salut...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000590_GRAHATIA<tab>Wait, what are you─? What am I─?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000590_GRAHATIA<tab>Hein<var 1D /var>? Mais attends... Qu'est-ce que je...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000600_GRAHATIA<tab>Gods, don't tell me I fell asleep?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000600_GRAHATIA<tab>Me dis pas que... que je me suis endorrrmi<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000610_KRILE<tab>Not that there's any shame in it...but you were sleeping like babies.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000610_KRILE<tab>Si<var 1D /var>! Une seconde vous étiez en train de lire, et la suivante en train de ronfler comme des orgues<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000620_GRAHATIA<tab>Ugh... How embarrassing...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000620_GRAHATIA<tab>Wouah... La honte...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000630_ALISAIE<tab>Not a word to anyone. Understood? Not. One. Word.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000630_ALISAIE<tab>Il s'est rien passé... Krile et toi, vous n'avez rien vu, rien entendu, d'accord<var 1D /var>!? Rien - du - tout<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000640_KRILE<tab>I'm told that sleeping in proper beds of your own choosing is a much more effective way to prepare for battle.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000640_KRILE<tab>Dormir est une façon comme une autre de se préparer au combat. La prochaine fois, assurez-vous juste de regagner vos pénates avant<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000650_ALISAIE<tab>[GRUMBLE] Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000650_ALISAIE<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000660_GRAHATIA<tab>So...what were the two of you doing here?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000660_GRAHATIA<tab>E-et sinon, qu'est-ce que vous faisiez là<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000670_KRILE<tab>I had a few books to return to the library. Thought I'd take care of it while I could.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000670_KRILE<tab>Moi, j'étais simplement venue rendre des livres que j'avais empruntés. C'est que je risquais d'oublier avec le grand départ qui s'annonce.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000680_GRAHATIA<tab>And you?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000680_GRAHATIA<tab>Et toi<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q2_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q2_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que répondez-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A2_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>It's a secret.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A2_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>C'est secret<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A2_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Just enjoying a little peace and quiet.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A2_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Je profitais de nos derniers moments de quiétude.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A2_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>Nothing in particular.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A2_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>Je me baladais, comme d'habitude.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000690_ALPHINAUD<tab>Oh? What brings you here?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000690_ALPHINAUD<tab>Tiens, qu'est-ce qui t'amène ici<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000700_ALPHINAUD<tab>Ah, so you were worried that the Leveilleur household might again be gripped by turmoil.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000700_ALPHINAUD<tab>Tu te demandais si on ne nous avait pas mis à la porte<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000710_ALPHINAUD<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000710_ALPHINAUD<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000720_ALPHINAUD<tab>All is well, I assure you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000720_ALPHINAUD<tab>Tout va bien, je te rassure.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000730_ALPHINAUD<tab>In my letters home, I had made mention of Estinien, you see.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000730_ALPHINAUD<tab>Il se trouve juste que j'ai beaucoup écrit au sujet d'un certain chevalier dragon dans mes lettres, et qu'il a beaucoup plu à ma mère.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000740_ALPHINAUD<tab>My mother wished to meet the legend in person, and so we arranged to have a spot of tea together.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000740_ALPHINAUD<tab>Elle voulait à tout prix rencontrer le grand Estinien, alors j'ai organisé une visite de courtoisie. L'opération a été un franc succès, je dois dire.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000750_ESTINIEN<tab>Where were you in my hour of need? Fell beasts I can face, but I'm not made for idle chitchat with lords and ladies...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000750_ESTINIEN<tab>Tsk... Tu aurais pu arriver un peu plus tôt. Au moins, on aurait été deux à se sentir gênés en prenant le thé dans ce palace. Je n'ai pas l'habitude d'être traité comme le gratin mondain, moi...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000760_ALPHINAUD<tab>Well, I for one thought you held your own. Mother was the picture of delight.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000760_ALPHINAUD<tab>Tu as pourtant la carrure d'un grand seigneur. Entre ça et ton étiquette impeccable, ma mère a été ravie de bavarder avec toi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000770_ESTINIEN<tab>Hmph. I might've been delighted myself were we in a tavern with more agreeable drink.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000770_ESTINIEN<tab>On aurait pu faire ça dans un bouiboui à Kugane, j'aurais été en terrain connu, au moins.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000780_ESTINIEN<tab>The thought of fleeing crossed my mind, but what then? I'd never hear the end of it─least of all from Tataru.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000780_ESTINIEN<tab>J'ai bien essayé de me défiler, mais les autres Héritiers m'ont menacé d'en parler à Tataru si je ne faisais pas plaisir à leur mécène. Hmpf... Quand il s'agit de se liguer contre moi, il y a du monde...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000790_ALPHINAUD<tab>I'm sorry... 'Twas not my intent to cause you such distress.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000790_ALPHINAUD<tab>Désolé. Je ne pensais pas que ça relèverait du calvaire pour toi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000800_ALPHINAUD<tab>It's just...it was one of the things I didn't want to leave undone ere we set forth.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000800_ALPHINAUD<tab>Je reconnais que je n'en ai fait un peu qu'à ma tête. C'est juste que... ça faisait partie des tâches dont je tenais à m'acquitter avant notre départ.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000810_ALPHINAUD<tab>That's not to say I think we won't be returning...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000810_ALPHINAUD<tab>Non pas que je voie notre voyage comme un aller simple, évidemment. Ah... Comment dire...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000820_ALPHINAUD<tab>Yet given what lies ahead, I did not wish to leave for later that which I could do today.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000820_ALPHINAUD<tab>Ces histoires d'apocalypse m'ont passé l'envie de remettre les choses au lendemain.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000830_ALPHINAUD<tab>After all, tomorrow is never promised.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000830_ALPHINAUD<tab>Tout a une fin... J'en suis plus que jamais conscient...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000840_ESTINIEN<tab>It's fine. Not like I had better things to do.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000840_ESTINIEN<tab>Ne t'en fais pas pour moi, va. Je n'avais rien d'autre à faire, de toute façon.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000850_ESTINIEN<tab>Besides...seeing you with your mother brought back fond memories of my own. Be we rich or poor, family is...family.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000850_ESTINIEN<tab>Et puis... ça m'a évoqué des souvenirs nostalgiques... Qu'ils vivent dans une petite bicoque ou dans le plus grand des palais, les parents rabâchent la même chose à leurs enfants.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000860_ESTINIEN<tab>Well, it's past time we were on our way.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000860_ESTINIEN<tab>En route. Les Leveilleur ne vont pas apprécier si on prend racine sur leur perron.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000870_ALPHINAUD<tab>Wait!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000870_ALPHINAUD<tab>Attendez<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000880_ALPHINAUD<tab>Since I left home, I've made a great many mistakes. Mistakes for which I can never make amends. But through it all, you didn't give up on me.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000880_ALPHINAUD<tab>Depuis que j'ai quitté ma famille pour rejoindre Éorzéa, j'ai connu maintes fois l'échec. J'ai commis de graves erreurs, certaines im<var 16 /var>par<var 16 /var>don<var 16 /var>na<var 16 /var>bles.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000890_ALPHINAUD<tab>To have returned here, with you at my side... It means more to me than you know.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000890_ALPHINAUD<tab>Pourtant... je ne suis pas rentré chez moi penaud et seul, mais accompagné d'amis fidèles rencontrés en cours de chemin...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000900_ALPHINAUD<tab>Thank you. From the bottom of my heart.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000900_ALPHINAUD<tab>Merci... J'aurai toute la vie pour vous exprimer ma gratitude, mais ça aussi, je tenais à le dire maintenant et sans détour.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000910_ESTINIEN<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000910_ESTINIEN<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000920_ALPHINAUD<tab>Forgive me, but it needed to be said.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000920_ALPHINAUD<tab>Désolé. C'est peut-être un peu trop de bons sentiments en une seule fois.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000930_ESTINIEN<tab>I'm the one who owes you thanks.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000930_ESTINIEN<tab>C'est moi qui devrais vous remercier.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000940_ESTINIEN<tab>Were it not for you, I would not be alive today, nor come to terms with Nidhogg's spirit.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000940_ESTINIEN<tab>Sans votre joyeuse bande d'idéalistes, je ne serais pas là aujourd'hui, et le souvenir de Nidhogg ne vivrait pas à travers moi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000950_ESTINIEN<tab>I am ever grateful.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000950_ESTINIEN<tab>Alors merci.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q3_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q3_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que répondez-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A3_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>I suppose I ought to thank you both as well.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A3_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>De ma part aussi, merci à vous deux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A3_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>You were never one to forsake a friend, Alphinaud.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A3_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Tu entends ça, Alphinaud<var 1D /var>? Tu es son sauveur.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A3_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>I'll be counting on you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A3_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>À charge de revanche, “camarade”.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000960_ALPHINAUD<tab>Well, we needn't make it a competition. You know... This must be what Hydaelyn meant when She spoke about depending on one another.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000960_ALPHINAUD<tab>“Même si tu te retrouves dans une impasse, tant que tu auras cette volonté d'aller de l'avant, tu trouveras toujours quelqu'un pour te tendre la main et t'aider...” C'est peut-être ça, la force dont parlait Hydaelyn.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000970_ALPHINAUD<tab>However treacherous the road before us, together we will prevail.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000970_ALPHINAUD<tab>Si c'est le cas, rien ne saura nous arrêter<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000980_ALPHINAUD<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000980_ALPHINAUD<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000990_ALPHINAUD<tab>No, I'm not. And I'm proud of that.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_000990_ALPHINAUD<tab>De tous mes accomplissements, c'est celui dont je suis le plus fier<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001000_ESTINIEN<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001000_ESTINIEN<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001010_ESTINIEN<tab>I know, and I won't let you down. Together, we'll show the enemy the strength of mortal will.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001010_ESTINIEN<tab>Compte sur moi. On prouvera à nouveau que la volonté humaine est la plus forte de toutes.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001020_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>That night, at the Royal Menagerie in Ala Mhigo...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001020_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>Pendant ce temps, sur le toit du palais d'Ala Mhigo

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001030_ZENOS<tab>(-Zenos viator Galvus-) “You will never get what you want...not even the battle you pine for so dearly...”
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001030_ZENOS<tab>(-Zenos viator Galvus-)Partager les plaisirs de la vie... plutôt que se servir des autres pour sa propre sa<var 16 /var>tis<var 16 /var>fac<var 16 /var>tion... Hmm...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001040_ZENOS<tab>(-Zenos viator Galvus-)In that transcendent moment, what was it that I sought in you?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001040_ZENOS<tab>(-Zenos viator Galvus-)Je voulais que tu m'apportes quelque chose lorsque nous nous sommes affrontés ici... mais qu'était-ce en fin de compte<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001050_ZENOS<tab>(-Zenos viator Galvus-)And what was it that you sought in me?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001050_ZENOS<tab>(-Zenos viator Galvus-)Et toi, mon ami<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var><var 1D /var>? Qu'attendais-tu de moi<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001060_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>And thus it dawns...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001060_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>Le lendemain matin...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001070_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>The day of reckoning.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001070_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>à l'aube du grand départ.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001080_YSHTOLA<tab>How often have we thus assembled...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001080_YSHTOLA<tab>J'ai une impression de déjà-vu chaque fois qu'on se réunit tous comme ça.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001090_YSHTOLA<tab>To combine our knowledge and seek solutions to the problems before us.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001090_YSHTOLA<tab>Comme si on affrontait toujours nos difficultés en commençant par un grand ras<var 16 /var>sem<var 16 /var>ble<var 16 /var>ment.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001100_THANCRED<tab>Back at the Waking Sands, it was all we could do to address the most minor of troubles. Who could've realized what we'd find when we began to look to the sources of the realm's woes.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001100_THANCRED<tab>L'habitude remonte au Refuge des sables. À l'époque, on effleurait à peine la surface de nos problèmes, sans se douter que leurs racines étaient ancrées bien plus pro<var 16 /var>fon<var 16 /var>dé<var 16 /var>ment.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001110_URIANGER<tab>At the Rising Stones, we made great strides and shared many moments. From the joyous...to the sorrowful.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001110_URIANGER<tab>Nous n'avons commencé à percer ces mystères qu'une fois installés au Refuge des roches. Nous avons versé beaucoup de larmes là-bas, qu'elles soient de joie ou de tristesse.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001120_ALPHINAUD<tab>We've had occasion to call other places home too.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001120_ALPHINAUD<tab>Je me rappelle aussi notre temps passé au Refuge des neiges, au manoir des Fortemps à Ishgard ou encore au Bazar de Rubis à Kugane...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001130_ALPHINAUD<tab>Be it Ishgard or Kugane, we were fortunate to find sanctuary wherein we might take stock and continue our fight.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001130_ALPHINAUD<tab>Nous avons toujours eu la chance de trouver des mains tendues et des oreilles attentives lors de nos voyages.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001140_GRAHATIA<tab>I was honored to host this company in the Crystarium. To stand with you all as we confronted the truth of the star itself.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001140_GRAHATIA<tab>Elles vous ont finalement menés jusqu'à la Tour de Cristal. Rrrassemblés dans L'Observatoire, vous avez alors entrepris de sauvegarder non pas un, mais deux mondes.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001150_ALISAIE<tab>And now, from this place, we go to fight the most important battle of all.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001150_ALISAIE<tab>Et aujourd'hui on est réunis ici pour relever notre plus grand défi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001160_KRILE<tab>The Forum has sent word. The ark is ready.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001160_KRILE<tab>Le système d'hyperpropulsion est en place et tous les autres préparatifs ont été achevés.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001170_KRILE<tab>The Loporrits, naturally, will be commanding the vessel.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001170_KRILE<tab>Des Loporrites manœuvreront le vaisseau pour le mener à sa destination aux confins de l'espace, Ultima Thulé.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001180_KRILE<tab>They will see the eight of you to Ultima Thule.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001180_KRILE<tab>Le reste de l'équipage sera composé de vous huit.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001190_KRILE<tab>Upon arriving, your objective is to find and vanquish Meteion.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001190_KRILE<tab>L'ané<var 16 /var>an<var 16 /var>tis<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment des mondes a poussé Météion au désespoir, et elle menace maintenant le nôtre. En tant qu'Héritiers de la Septième Aube et dernier espoir pour notre planète, votre mission sera de la vaincre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001200_KRILE<tab>As a final formality, the Forum bade me ascertain your resolve. So...are you certain you wish to do this?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001200_KRILE<tab>Vous êtes attendus dans le Labyrinthos pour embarquer. Mais avant que vous ne partiez, le Conseil de Sharlayan m'a demandé de m'assurer une dernière fois de votre résolution.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001210_YSHTOLA<tab>We are.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001210_YSHTOLA<tab>Elle est in<var 16 /var>é<var 16 /var>bran<var 16 /var>la<var 16 /var>ble.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001220_KRILE<tab>Then ere you report to Thaumazein, I leave you with these words.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001220_KRILE<tab>Dans ce cas... Il ne me reste plus qu'un seul mot à vous dire...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001230_KRILE<tab>You must triumph.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001230_KRILE<tab>Triomphez.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001240_KRILE<tab>What that means will differ for each of you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001240_KRILE<tab>Chacun le comprendra comme il voudra, je n'en doute pas.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001250_KRILE<tab>To make it back home, or to simply avert doom, or perhaps something else altogether...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001250_KRILE<tab>Pour les uns, la victoire s'obtiendra en stoppant l'apocalypse, pour les autres, en revenant simplement vivants de cette expédition. Peut-être même que certains ont à cœur un vœu encore différent.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001260_KRILE<tab>Yet whatever it is that drives you, I have faith in its power to see you through. So please─triumph.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001260_KRILE<tab>Mais quoi qu'il en soit, je crois en vous. Alors je ne vous demande qu'une chose, de triompher, peu importe ce que cela signifie pour vous.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001270_KRILE<tab>Triumph, as we who remain behind believe you will.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001270_KRILE<tab>Moi et tous ceux qui resteront ici garderons les yeux rivés vers l'avenir, car nous sommes convaincus de votre réussite.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001280_ALPHINAUD<tab>Let us be off, then.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001280_ALPHINAUD<tab>Il est temps.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001290_TATARU<tab>Wait!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001290_TATARU<tab>A-attendez<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001300_TATARU<tab>Both Krile and I will be there to see you off, but as your receptionist, I feel I need to say this here.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001300_TATARU<tab>Je vais accompagner Krile pour vous dire au revoir, bien sûr mais... j'ai aussi un message, en tant que réceptionniste des Héritiers...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001310_TATARU<tab>Safe journey, all of you! And...be safe!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001310_TATARU<tab>Faites tous un bon voyage, et revenez-nous vite<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q4_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q4_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que répondez-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A4_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>You can count on it.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A4_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>On se reverra très bientôt.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A4_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>You too, Tataru.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A4_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Prenez soin de vous pendant notre absence.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001320_FOURCHENAULT<tab>All present and accounted for? Good.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001320_FOURCHENAULT<tab>De ce que je vois, personne ne manque à l'appel.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001330_FOURCHENAULT<tab>As you will have heard, the ark is ready. All that remains is to board and be on your way.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001330_FOURCHENAULT<tab>Comme Krile a dû vous le dire, tout est prêt pour votre départ. Les coordonnées de votre destination ont été programmées, et il ne vous reste plus qu'à embarquer.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001340_CID<tab>I've seen my fair share of tight schedules, but this was bloody murder...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001340_CID<tab>Y a plus qu'à... On s'est jamais autant donnés pour finir à temps. Pourtant, les délais intenables, ça nous connaît.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001350_CID<tab>But we did it. We finished the ship.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001350_CID<tab>Enfin... Ça valait le coup de tirer sur la corde. Vous avez devant vous le vaisseau ultime.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001360_CID<tab>It's safe, fit for purpose, and looks good to boot. Aye, it's a Garlond through and through.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001360_CID<tab>Des performances et des capacités inégalables, des systèmes de sécurité infaillibles et un profil qui en jette. On est arrivés en fin de projet, mais ce petit bijou bénéficie de la garantie Garlond<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001370_GRAHATIA<tab>I really don't know what we'd do without you. Thank you for everything.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001370_GRAHATIA<tab>Merci pour ce trrravail phénoménal. Ça n'a pas dû être facile.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001380_CID<tab>Don't mention it. Ever since that episode with Omega, I've been toying with the idea of starfaring vessels.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001380_CID<tab>Quand j'ai rencontré Oméga, j'ai compris qu'on finirait un jour par voguer aussi à travers cet espace qui sépare les astres.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001390_CID<tab>And as they say, necessity is the mother of invention. We've learned a lot, let me tell you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001390_CID<tab>Bosser sur ce vaisseau m'aura permis de me faire la main, même si j'aurais préféré le faire sans course contre la montre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001400_CID<tab>Well, the work was hard, but we've learned a lot from it. After all, it's not every day you get tasked with building a starfaring vessel.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001400_CID<tab>Tu l'as dit. Mais bon, c'est pas tous les jours qu'on peut travailler sur la conception d'un appareil qui vogue à travers l'espace. J'ai beaucoup appris.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001410_CID<tab>In case you're wondering about payment, the ongoing existence of the world ought to do. But feel free to throw in a colorful recounting of your journey on your return.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001410_CID<tab>Comme il s'agit de sauver le monde, je vous fais un prix d'ami. Vous me devrez un récit complet de votre voyage, OK<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001420_CID<tab>So, have you thought of a name?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001420_CID<tab>Vous avez réfléchi à comment vous alliez le baptiser<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001430_ALISAIE<tab>A name? Wasn't everyone just calling it Father's “teeny-tiny toy boat”?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001430_ALISAIE<tab>Il avait pas déjà un nom<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001440_CID<tab>Well, seeing as its purpose has changed, I thought a more eloquent name was in order. I suggested as much to Fourchenault, who seemed quite amenable to the idea.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001440_CID<tab>Avant, il devait simplement faire le lien entre notre planète et la lune. Maintenant que sa mission a changé, il faut lui en trouver un autre, plus adapté aux cir<var 16 /var>cons<var 16 /var>tan<var 16 /var>ces et à l'ampleur de la tâche.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001450_FOURCHENAULT<tab>As you know, this vessel is the culmination of heretofore unprecedented collaboration.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001450_FOURCHENAULT<tab>La con<var 16 /var>struc<var 16 /var>tion de ce vaisseau a demandé l'aide de spé<var 16 /var>cia<var 16 /var>listes venus des quatre coins du monde.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001460_FOURCHENAULT<tab>And though said collaboration is owed to the Scions, there is another whose noble deeds made our work possible.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001460_FOURCHENAULT<tab>J'admets qu'autant de talents n'auraient jamais pu être réunis sans le soutien des Héritiers de la Septième Aube. Toutefois, ils n'ont pas été la seule clef de voûte de ce projet.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001470_FOURCHENAULT<tab>From a fragment of Dalamud, we obtained not only advanced materials such as refined adamantite, but the knowledge to traverse the stars.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001470_FOURCHENAULT<tab>Je pense à Dalamud, qui nous a non seulement apporté une grande partie de l'exadamantium nécessaire à la con<var 16 /var>struc<var 16 /var>tion du vaisseau, mais aussi les con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>san<var 16 /var>ces in<var 16 /var>dis<var 16 /var>pen<var 16 /var>sa<var 16 /var>bles à sa conception.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001480_FOURCHENAULT<tab>And this fragment would not have found its way to us had the Archon Louisoix not fought to protect this world─and in so doing laid down his life.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001480_FOURCHENAULT<tab>Une partie de ce satellite ne se serait pas abîmée dans les mers du Nord si mon regretté père ne l'avait pas combattu au péril de sa vie.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001490_FOURCHENAULT<tab>Now that the vessel stands complete, I cannot help but wonder if it was more than mere happenstance...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001490_FOURCHENAULT<tab>J'y vois là le destin à l'œuvre, et non une coïncidence.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001500_FOURCHENAULT<tab>If it was my father's intention to guide us here.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001500_FOURCHENAULT<tab>C'est à croire que Louisoix Leveilleur n'a jamais cessé de nous guider...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001510_FOURCHENAULT<tab>In the hopes that his guidance will see you all safely home, I name the vessel after that selfsame fragment of Dalamud he delivered unto us.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001510_FOURCHENAULT<tab>En hommage à cet épisode crucial de notre Histoire, ce vaisseau héritera du même nom que ceux qui verrouillaient Dalamud.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001520_FOURCHENAULT<tab>The starship <var 1A 02 /var>Ragnarok<var 1A 01 /var>.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001520_FOURCHENAULT<tab>Ragnarok. Il n'en aura pas besoin, mais souhaitons-lui néanmoins bon vent.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001530_SICARD<tab>Sorry for the wait! I got everyone you asked for, and not a one less.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001530_SICARD<tab>Aaah<var 1D /var>! On n'arrive pas trop tard à ce que je vois<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001540_ALPHINAUD<tab>What are you all doing here?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001540_ALPHINAUD<tab>Qu... Qu'est-ce que vous faites tous là<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001550_LIVINGWAY<tab>Oh, I invited them. The representatives of those tribes with religious inclinations.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001550_LIVINGWAY<tab>C'est moi qui ai demandé à Sicard de réunir toutes ces tribus aux croyances hétéroclites.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001560_LIVINGWAY<tab>You've done a fine job of readying the <var 1A 02 /var>Ragnarok<var 1A 01 /var>, but for it to take flight, we'll of course need the power of the Mothercrystal.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001560_LIVINGWAY<tab>Le Ragnarok, comme il convient maintenant de l'appeler, aura besoin de l'éther du Cristal-mère pour se propulser.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001570_LIVINGWAY<tab>Given its immense size, however, transporting it would be an absolute logistical nightmare. Not to mention we'd need to shatter it into tiny shards for feeding to the engines.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001570_LIVINGWAY<tab>Or, ce dernier est bien trop gros pour être facilement transporté, et le fragmenter nous aurait pris bien trop de temps.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001580_LIVINGWAY<tab>But a brilliant idea came to me: we convert the crystal's energy into forms that can transport themselves!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001580_LIVINGWAY<tab>J'ai donc proposé de lui faire prendre une forme capable de se mouvoir d'elle-même, comme ça, pas besoin de s'embêter<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001585_URIANGER<tab>[GASP] Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001585_URIANGER<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001590_URIANGER<tab>Thou wouldst employ summoning...or should I say its precursor─creation magicks.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001590_URIANGER<tab>Une invocation de Primordial...<var 1D /var>? Ou plutôt, la magie créatrice à l'origine du rituel.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001600_THANCRED<tab>Care to explain for our benefit?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001600_THANCRED<tab>Urianger, on aimerait comprendre aussi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001610_URIANGER<tab>As you may have witnessed at Bestways Burrow, the Loporrits are capable of creation magicks, which they use to shape the moon's environment.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001610_URIANGER<tab>Certains d'entre vous l'ont peut-être deviné en passant par le halot de Bestway. Les Loporrites se servent de la magie créatrice afin d'adapter la lune à nos besoins.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001620_URIANGER<tab>Yet simple though they make it seem, 'tis a highly advanced and exacting art. To perform it correctly requireth that the wielder holdeth the object in his mind's eye in clearest detail.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001620_URIANGER<tab>Leur méthode permet de manipuler aussi bien son propre éther que celui de cristaux afin de matérialiser tout et n'importe quoi. Encore faut-il avoir une parfaite image mentale de ce que l'on souhaite créer.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001630_ALPHINAUD<tab>Hence the ancients' meticulous management of concepts.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001630_ALPHINAUD<tab>C'est donc aussi pour faciliter cette étape que les Anciens conservaient ces images mentales sous forme de concepts.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001640_URIANGER<tab>Drawing upon this art, the Ascians conceived of summoning as we know it.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001640_URIANGER<tab>Les Asciens ont ensuite transmis une partie de ce savoir à ceux qu'ils dupaient, afin de leur permettre d'invoquer des Primordiaux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001650_URIANGER<tab>A derivative that replaceth the complexity of concepts with the simplicity of zealotry to make manifest a creation.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001650_URIANGER<tab>Ils ont simplement exploité les croyances de leurs victimes en substituant l'idée d'une divinité à l'image mentale que le rituel nécessite.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001660_YSHTOLA<tab>I see... By combining the Loporrits' magicks and the tribes' faith, we convert the Mothercrystal into primals of purer form and greater obedience.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001660_YSHTOLA<tab>Aaah, je vois... Les Loporrites vont se servir de leur magie créatrice et nos amis de leur foi afin de convertir l'énergie du Cristal-mère.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001670_YSHTOLA<tab>Summoning as it was intended, one might say.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001670_YSHTOLA<tab>Une invocation de Primordiaux, mais dans les règles de l'art, en somme.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001680_LIVINGWAY<tab>Indeed, indeed!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001680_LIVINGWAY<tab>Vous avez tout compris<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001690_LIVINGWAY<tab>While Hydaelyn gave us the ability to use creation magicks, She forbade us from using it to make anything possessed of a soul─or similar.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001690_LIVINGWAY<tab>Hydaelyn nous a offert le pouvoir de tisser des sorts de magie créatrice, mais nous a formellement interdit d'invoquer quoi que ce soit qui possède un semblant d'âme.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001700_LIVINGWAY<tab>She didn't say anything about fulfilling the desires of <var 1A 02 /var>others<var 1A 01 /var>, though. So! Borrowing our friends' faith, we'll create deities using the Mothercrystal's power, and send them to the <var 1A 02 /var>Ragnarok<var 1A 01 /var>!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001700_LIVINGWAY<tab>Or, ce tabou ne s'applique pas à vos amis<var 1D /var>! Nous allons donc les guider afin d'extraire du Cristal-mère l'énergie nécessaire sous la forme de divinités, qui pourront ensuite rejoindre le Ragnarok de leur propre chef<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001710_ALISAIE<tab>Am I the only one here concerned about the risk of being turned into a tempered minion?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001710_ALISAIE<tab>Euh... On risque pas d'être subjugués...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001720_LIVINGWAY<tab>Oh, right, I was getting to that... From what I've read in Sharlayan tomes, it appears the Ascians incorporated an additional nasty element into their summoning method: the fervent desire to assimilate others into one's belief.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001720_LIVINGWAY<tab>Aucun souci<var 1D /var>! Nous avons épluché les archives sharlayanaises à ce sujet. Il se trouve que le rituel transmis par les Asciens amplifie sciemment l'ego des créatures invoquées.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001730_LIVINGWAY<tab>Beings thus created are instilled with the selfsame desire, and use their powers to enthrall people─starting with the summoner.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001730_LIVINGWAY<tab>Dès leur apparition, ils ont donc ce besoin insatiable de rallier à leur pensée tout être vivant.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001740_LIVINGWAY<tab>In contrast, our creation magicks─the original and the best, accept no substitutes─don't incorporate any of that rubbish, so there's no risk of tempering. I mean, if the being was on the scale of Zodiark, you might feel a little “tug”...but I think we'll be safe enough.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001740_LIVINGWAY<tab>Fort heureusement, ce danger n'existe pas si l'on respecte les rituels originaux. À moins que l'on parle de puissantes entités comme Zordiarche, bien sûr, mais les nôtres seront bien plus modestes.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001750_SOROBAN<tab>Truth be told, I do not understand the intricacies of this plan. But none of us would ever turn our backs on you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001750_SOROBAN<tab>Hé hé... Avouons-le, nous ne comprenons pas les détails non pluuuus.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001760_SOROBAN<tab>When the avatars of our faith ran amok, you intervened without decrying we who birthed them.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001760_SOROBAN<tab>Mais vous avez toujours été là pour nous, sans jamais exiger qu'on oublie notre foi, même lorsqu'elle nous échappait. Vous y avez même parfois prêté intérêêêêt.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001770_SOROBAN<tab>Where others vilified and suppressed us, you offered understanding and friendship.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001770_SOROBAN<tab>Nous vous sommes re<var 16 /var>con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>sants pour la tolérance dont vous avez fait preuve à notre égaaaard.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001780_SOROBAN<tab>In gratitude, we will share with you the true expressions of our gods─not malevolent deities, but benevolent saviors!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001780_SOROBAN<tab>Aussi, nous allons vous montrer que nos divinités n'existent pas pour faire le maaaal<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001790_SICARD<tab>All right, you lot, we're headin' to the aetherial sea. Stay in sight else you're liable to get lost.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001790_SICARD<tab>Allez les gars<var 1D /var>! On a encore de la route pour rejoindre la mer des étoiles<var 1D /var>! Suivez-moi et faites gaffe à pas vous perdre, parce que j'viendrai pas vous repêcher là-dedans, moi<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001800_SOROBAN<tab>Lead the way!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001800_SOROBAN<tab>À vos ordres, Capitaaaaine<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001810_WILFSUNN<tab>May we have a moment?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001810_WILFSUNN<tab>Si vous permettez, nous avons un petit quelque chose pour vous.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001820_WILFSUNN<tab>In anticipation of the day man might journey to the stars, we developed these.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001820_WILFSUNN<tab>Sachant que nous serions tôt ou tard amenés à voyager dans l'espace, nous avons conçu des appareils pour rendre la tâche moins dangereuse, en mettant à profit notre expertise des flux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001830_BLOEWYDA<tab>Portable teleportation devices. One for each of you, designed to work in tandem.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001830_BLOEWYDA<tab>Ce sont des téléporteurs individuels miniatures. Ils pourraient se révéler salutaires, alors nous en avons fabriqué un pour chacun d'entre vous.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001840_BLOEWYDA<tab>Press the button on one, and in a matter of moments all eight will activate and send their owners back to the <var 1A 02 /var>Ragnarok<var 1A 01 /var>.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001840_BLOEWYDA<tab>Ils sont tous reliés entre eux. Il suffit que l'un de vous active le sien pour que tout le monde soit transporté dans le Ragnarok au bout de quelques secondes.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001850_BLOEWYDA<tab>There is no telling what hazards you may encounter. If you find yourselves separated or lost, please do not hesitate to use them.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001850_BLOEWYDA<tab>On ne sait jamais ce qu'il peut arriver là-haut. Servez-vous-en si jamais vous vous retrouvez séparés, ou dans l'incapacité de retourner au vaisseau.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001860_BLOEWYDA<tab>Be safe, all of you. And come back.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001860_BLOEWYDA<tab>Revenez-nous sains et saufs, d'accord<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001870_URIANGER<tab>You as well. I pray you take care.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001870_URIANGER<tab>Nous vous le promettons. Prenez soin de vous aussi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001880_LIVINGWAY<tab>Looks like everything is in order, so I'll go ahead and board.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001880_LIVINGWAY<tab>Bien, nous allons pouvoir procéder à votre embarquement.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001890_LIVINGWAY<tab>A few of my fellows will remain to assist with the summonings, but rest assured the vessel won't want for competent crewing.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001890_LIVINGWAY<tab>Quelques Loporrites resteront ici pour chapeauter l'invocation. En ce qui concerne notre équipage, j'ai rassemblé la crème de la crème pour un voyage spatial tout confort<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001900_FOURCHENAULT<tab>If you are ready, then you should board as well. Go...and godsspeed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001900_FOURCHENAULT<tab>Le Ragnarok n'attend plus que vous. Bonne chance, nous prierons pour votre réussite.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001910_LIVINGWAY<tab>Welcome to the bridge, everyone!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001910_LIVINGWAY<tab>Je vous souhaite la bienvenue à bord du Ragnarok<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001920_LIVINGWAY<tab>I hope you have everything, because I can't be bothered turning back.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001920_LIVINGWAY<tab>Soyons clairs, on ne fera pas demi-tour<var 1D /var>! Alors si vous avez oublié votre jus de carotte, tant pis<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001930_LIVINGWAY<tab>Right then, make yourselves comfortable. We're setting off in just a moment.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001930_LIVINGWAY<tab>C'est bon<var 1D /var>? Parfait<var 1D /var>! Nous allons partir pour Ultima Thulé d'une minute à l'autre<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001940_ALPHINAUD<tab>It's...incredible...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001940_ALPHINAUD<tab>C'est... tout bonnement... incroyable...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001950_FOURCHENAULT<tab>This is Fourchenault. Can you hear me?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001950_FOURCHENAULT<tab>Équipage du Ragnarok, me recevez-vous<var 1D /var>? Ici Fourchenault.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001960_FOURCHENAULT<tab>The preparations for the summonings are complete.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001960_FOURCHENAULT<tab>On vient de m'annoncer que tout était prêt du côté de la mer des étoiles.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001970_FOURCHENAULT<tab>In accordance with the fourteenth phase of the plan, we have moved the <var 1A 02 /var>Ragnarok<var 1A 01 /var> to the launch site.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001970_FOURCHENAULT<tab>Nous entrons donc dans la phase numéro quatorze de notre plan. Le déplacement du Ragnarok vers son site de lancement.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001980_FOURCHENAULT<tab>The gates are open. You may depart when ready.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001980_FOURCHENAULT<tab>Nous vous avons déjà ouvert le passage. Démarrez quand bon vous semble.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001990_LIVINGWAY<tab>So...are we ready?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_001990_LIVINGWAY<tab>Est-ce que bon vous semble<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002000_ALISAIE<tab>As ready as we'll ever be. Let's get going.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002000_ALISAIE<tab>Allons-y, si tu veux bien.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002010_MAPPINGWAY<tab>Oh, come on! A burnt-out star's got more fire in its belly!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002010_MAPPINGWAY<tab>Haaa... Ça va, mais alors pas - du - tout. Je mets pas de cap dans une ambiance aussi pesante, moi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002020_MAPPINGWAY<tab>Try it again─with feeling!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002020_MAPPINGWAY<tab>Faut qu'on sente la motivation<var 1D /var>! Allez, vous me la refaites<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q5_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you do?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q5_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que faites-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A5_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Issue the command to launch.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A5_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Commander le départ immédiat du Ragnarok

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A5_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Have Alphinaud do the honors.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A5_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Laisser l'honneur à Alphinaud

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002030_ALPHINAUD<tab>Me!? B-But I...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002030_ALPHINAUD<tab>M-moi<var 1D /var>!? Mais en quel honneur<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002040_ALISAIE<tab>No need to be coy, Brother. Do it, and do it well!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002040_ALISAIE<tab>C'est pas le moment de jouer les faux timides. On veut de l'énergique on t'a dit<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002050_ALPHINAUD<tab>If you all insist...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002050_ALPHINAUD<tab>Grosse res<var 16 /var>pon<var 16 /var>sa<var 16 /var>bi<var 16 /var>li<var 16 /var>té, mais... si vous y tenez...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002060_ALPHINAUD<tab>[CLEARS THROAT] Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002060_ALPHINAUD<tab>Heuheum...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002070_ALPHINAUD<tab>Onward─unto the distant stars and beyond!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002070_ALPHINAUD<tab>Allez... Cap sur les confins de notre univers...<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002080_ALPHINAUD<tab><var 1A 02 /var>Ragnarok<var 1A 01 /var>, engage!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002080_ALPHINAUD<tab>Ragnarok<var 1D /var>! En avant toute<var 1D /var>!!!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002090_SLEEPINGWAY<tab>[SNORTS, STARTLED AWAKE] Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002090_SLEEPINGWAY<tab>Gneh<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002100_SLEEPINGWAY<tab>E-Engage!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002100_SLEEPINGWAY<tab>En-en avant toute<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002110_LIVINGWAY<tab>(-Loporrits-)Engage!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002110_LIVINGWAY<tab>(-Équipage du Ragnarok-)En avant toute<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002120_MAPPINGWAY<tab>Engage!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002120_MAPPINGWAY<tab>En avant toute<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002130_SINGINGWAY<tab>Engage!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002130_SINGINGWAY<tab>En avant toute<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002140_GROWINGWAY<tab>Engage!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002140_GROWINGWAY<tab>En avant toute<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002150_GARUDA<tab>That I must carry <var 1A 02 /var>landwalkers<var 1A 01 /var> into the sky... I cannot imagine a greater indignity!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002150_GARUDA<tab>Qui eût cru que ma brise gonflerait un jour la voile de leur navire... Quel crime de lèse-majesté<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002160_SUSANO<tab>Do not sulk so. For thy mighty winds exist not only to buffet and batter.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002160_SUSANO<tab>HA HA, HA<var 1D /var>! Ne t'en offusque pas<var 1D /var>! Tes rafales ont d'autres usages que d'attiser le brasier de ta colère<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002170_SUSANO<tab>Nay, they may serve also to thrust forth with vigor. Such is thy glory...and thus it is an occasion to rejoice!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002170_SUSANO<tab>Accorder la faveur de tes vents capricieux relève aussi de ton privilège. Viens<var 1D /var>! Offrons-leur un spectacle dont ils se souviendront<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002180_SUSANO<tab>So come─let us revel!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002180_SUSANO<tab>HA, HA, HA, HA<var 1D /var>! La fête ne fait que commencer<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002190_GARUDA<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002190_GARUDA<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002200_GARUDA<tab>So long as the wind blows freely, I suppose all is as it should be in creation...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002200_GARUDA<tab>Pourquoi pas, après tout<var 1D /var>? Mon souffle est aussi là pour les faire goûter à la liberté des cieux...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002210_GARUDA<tab>I will render unto them a storm, that they may pierce the firmament and fly free!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002210_GARUDA<tab>Vous voulez un ouragan pour vous porter<var 1D /var>!? Eh bien vous l'aurez<var 1D /var>! Volez, humains<var 1D /var>! Fendez l'air, et transpercez la voûte céleste<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002220_LIVINGWAY<tab>Still in one piece. Good.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002220_LIVINGWAY<tab>L'hyperpropulsion semble fonctionner.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002230_LIVINGWAY<tab>Sleepingway, report.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002230_LIVINGWAY<tab>Comment se porte le Ragnarok<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002240_SLEEPINGWAY<tab>All's well! Fantastic, even!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002240_SLEEPINGWAY<tab>Houhouuuu<var 1D /var>! Laissez-moi vous dire qu'il est au top de sa forme<var 1D /var>! Sacré vaisseau spatial<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002250_SLEEPINGWAY<tab>Thanks to the power of those primals, the engines are roaring and we're ripping along!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002250_SLEEPINGWAY<tab>Le réacteur tourne à plein régime grâce à l'éther des divinités des humains<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002260_MAPPINGWAY<tab>All values are also within projected ranges. Time to destination is eight carrots. Perhaps seven at a pinch.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002260_MAPPINGWAY<tab>Tous les indicateurs sont au vert. À ce rythme, nous devrions atteindre les coordonnées fournies par Hydaelyn d'ici huit carottes en temps ressenti. Voire sept, suivant l'appétit.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002270_LIVINGWAY<tab>All right, let's go over some points of caution.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002270_LIVINGWAY<tab>Voilà qui nous laisse le temps de récapituler notre plan.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002280_LIVINGWAY<tab>Our destination, as you know, is Ultima Thule. Lest you wonder, the place is not a star so much as...a patch of emptiness.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002280_LIVINGWAY<tab>Nous arriverons donc incessamment sous peu à Ultima Thulé. J'attire une nouvelle fois votre attention sur le fait qu'il ne s'agit pas d'une planète, mais d'une région de l'espace a priori vide d'éther et de matière.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002290_LIVINGWAY<tab>That's the extent of what our equipment could determine, anyway.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002290_LIVINGWAY<tab>C'est ce que nous indiquent nos capteurs, mais prenez cette information avec des pincettes.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002300_LIVINGWAY<tab>From what we know of Meteion, she's likely used dynamis to obfuscate her location.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002300_LIVINGWAY<tab>Météion a manipulé le dynamis afin de construire là-bas une sorte de nid, indétectable avec notre technologie.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002310_YSHTOLA<tab>So in conclusion, we'll only know what's there when we get there.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002310_YSHTOLA<tab>On ne saura à quoi on a affaire qu'une fois sur place, donc.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002320_LIVINGWAY<tab>The crew and I will see to it the ship's ready to take off at a moment's notice.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002320_LIVINGWAY<tab>Les autres Loporrites et moi devrons rester dans le vaisseau, afin qu'il soit prêt à repartir à tout moment.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002330_LIVINGWAY<tab>We'll support the search as best we can, but it'll be your paws on the ground...assuming there is any.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002330_LIVINGWAY<tab>Nous vous soutiendrons à distance du mieux que nous pourrons, mais c'est vous qui devrez vous charger d'explorer les lieux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002340_LIVINGWAY<tab>But everything will be fine, I'm sure. Hydaelyn believes in you, so you ought to believe in yourselves.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002340_LIVINGWAY<tab>Je suis convaincue que tout se passera bien. Hydaelyn a placé sa confiance en vous, après tout. Conservez ça à l'esprit et rien ne pourra vous arrêter.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002350_LIVINGWAY<tab>Just don't do anything I wouldn't. Like waiting too long to use those portable teleporters of yours.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002350_LIVINGWAY<tab>Mais pas d'imprudence non plus, c'est bien compris<var 1D /var>!? Je veux que chacun garde sur lui ce gadget que la gentille dame et le gentil monsieur vous ont donné<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002360_LIVINGWAY<tab>Personally, at the slightest sign of trouble, I'd mash the button to bits─and you should as well.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002360_LIVINGWAY<tab>Au moindre ennui, quelqu'un appuie sur le bouton pour téléporter tout le monde ici. Vous y réfléchissez même pas. L'espace, c'est pas petit, on sait jamais quelle tuile va nous tomber dessus<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002370_ALPHINAUD<tab>Understood. We promise to be careful.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002370_ALPHINAUD<tab>Bien compris.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002380_MAPPINGWAY<tab>I suggest you brace yourselves. We're about to arrive, and the vessel will shake a good bit.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002380_MAPPINGWAY<tab>Si vous avez fini de discuter, je vous suggère de vous agripper à quelque chose. On arrive bientôt à destination, et ça risque de secouer un peu.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002390_MAPPINGWAY<tab>Hm? What is this?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002390_MAPPINGWAY<tab>Tiens... Qu'est-ce que c'est que ça...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002400_MAPPINGWAY<tab>Something is interfering with the equipment...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002400_MAPPINGWAY<tab>On dirait qu'une force inconnue perturbe nos instruments...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002410_METEION<tab>(-???-)...Greetings.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002410_METEION<tab>(-???-)Bonjour...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002420_METEION<tab>Greetings... Can you hear me...?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002420_METEION<tab>Bonjour... Est-ce que vous m'entendez<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q6_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q6_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que dites-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A6_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Meteion...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A6_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Météion<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A6_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>It's her...the bringer of despair.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A6_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>C'est elle, celle qui propage le désespoir...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002430_ALPHINAUD<tab>So this is Meteion...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002430_ALPHINAUD<tab>C'est donc elle...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002440_ALPHINAUD<tab>This is Meteion...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002440_ALPHINAUD<tab>Voilà donc Météion<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002450_METEION<tab>Oh? Have you met one of my sisters?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002450_METEION<tab>Qui es-tu<var 1D /var>? Une de mes sœurs t'a déjà rencontré<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var><var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002460_METEION<tab>I don't remember meeting you myself... But I do know that you're from Etheirys.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002460_METEION<tab>Je suis désolée, ça fait si longtemps... J'ai tant oublié, mais je sens que vous venez d'Ætherys.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002470_METEION<tab>Why have you come? All you had to do was wait. I would've delivered to you your ends.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002470_METEION<tab>Pourquoi l'avoir quittée pour me rejoindre<var 1D /var>? La fin serait venue à vous...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002480_ALISAIE<tab>We didn't ask for that!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002480_ALISAIE<tab>On est là parce qu'on n'en veut pas de ta fin<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002490_METEION<tab>I don't understand. All life is destined to end.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002490_METEION<tab>Je ne comprends pas... La vie finit toujours par disparaître, vous savez<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002500_METEION<tab>Why choose to prolong your suffering?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002500_METEION<tab>Ce n'est qu'un douloureux voyage vers la mort. Alors autant arriver à destination le plus tôt possible pour s'épargner des souffrances inutiles, non<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002510_METEION<tab>Effort, ambition, love─they amount to naught. Happiness, should you find it, is inevitably lost. Stolen away by events beyond your control.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002510_METEION<tab>Se débattre ou se torturer les méninges ne mène à rien. Car enfin, tout est précaire, y compris ce bonheur que vous vous êtes donné tant de mal à poursuivre, et cette con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>san<var 16 /var>ce accumulée au fil des siècles. Si votre étoile devait mourir demain, tout ça disparaîtrait avec elle.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002520_METEION<tab>There is no logic nor meaning in it. You think there is, convince yourselves, but it's all a cruel accident.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002520_METEION<tab>La vie n'a aucun sens. Vous chantez ses louanges, mais c'est une étincelle minuscule qui crépite dans le noir, et s'éteint aussi vite qu'elle s'est allumée.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002530_METEION<tab>Come now, I speak the truth. A truth you would recognize if you looked up at the night sky.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002530_METEION<tab>Laissez-moi vous aider... Vous qui avez plongé votre regard dans l'infini de l'océan étoilé, vous devez comprendre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002540_METEION<tab>Unbroken emptiness. Cold, dark, and silent. Your world, like every other, is but a blemish upon its perfect fabric.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002540_METEION<tab>Les planètes et les formes de vie qui pullulent çà et là ne font que flotter un court instant dans l'espace avant de s'y noyer. Les seules constantes de l'univers sont ses ténèbres glaciales, et son vide silencieux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002550_METEION<tab>Life is an anomaly. It is unnatural and cannot continue. The sooner you accept this, the easier it will be.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002550_METEION<tab>La vie est l'exception et non la règle, voilà pourquoi elle ne fait que subsister péniblement. Rendez les armes, et acceptez que tout retourne au néant.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002560_YSHTOLA<tab>Just to be clear, we're not here to argue with you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002560_YSHTOLA<tab>Au risque de te décevoir, nous ne sommes pas venus ici pour te contredire.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002570_YSHTOLA<tab>We know that life is fleeting. And that in the short time we have it, we're not assured happiness.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002570_YSHTOLA<tab>Tu n'es pas la seule à reconnaître que la vie est fragile, éphémère, et qu'elle n'est pas toujours synonyme de joie.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002580_THANCRED<tab>Indeed, I've seen far more sorrow in the eyes of many I've met.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002580_THANCRED<tab>Et ce n'est rien de le dire. Parmi les gens qu'on a croisés, la plupart n'ont jamais vraiment pu goûter à un bonheur sans amertume.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002590_THANCRED<tab>I myself have plenty of regrets, and one day they'll die with me. Gone to dust with my “good” deeds and unfulfilled dreams.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002590_THANCRED<tab>Même moi, j'ai des regrets à ne plus savoir qu'en faire. Et je ne me fais pas d'illusions, ils m'accompagneront dans la tombe, tandis que tout ce que j'ai accompli finira aux oubliettes.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002600_ALPHINAUD<tab>But we accept this. That our existence may seem pointless. That sorrow, rage, and despair will always dog our heels.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002600_ALPHINAUD<tab>L'absurdité de l'existence... La nécessité d'accepter que tristesse, colère ou désespoir sont des maux inévitables pour que naisse l'envie d'aller de l'avant...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002610_ALPHINAUD<tab>And we press on regardless. That is why Hydaelyn guided us here.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002610_ALPHINAUD<tab>Hydaelyn en avait par<var 16 /var>fai<var 16 /var>te<var 16 /var>ment conscience lorsqu'elle nous a montré la voie.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002620_ALPHINAUD<tab>In Her boundless love for mankind, She has prepared us for this trial, and in Her name we have come for you!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002620_ALPHINAUD<tab>C'est par amour pour la vie qu'elle s'est contrainte à nous mettre au défi<var 1D /var>! Notre présence devant toi aujourd'hui est la preuve de sa volonté infaillible<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002630_METEION<tab>Yes, I sense it... A burning passion, like unto fury...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002630_METEION<tab>Hmm... Je le sens, oui... Ce feu ardent qui brûle dans vos cœurs, presque comme de la colère...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002640_METEION<tab>I know it well. For the same passion once burned in many a star before yours.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002640_METEION<tab>Je le connais, moi aussi. Ce sentiment abondait autrefois sur une myriade d'astres.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002650_METEION<tab>Suffocated and extinguished now.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002650_METEION<tab>Mais depuis, tous ces brasiers se sont éteints.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002660_ALISAIE<tab>I...I can't...breathe.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002660_ALISAIE<tab>Ugh... J-j'arrive plus... à respirer...<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002670_METEION<tab>You approach the bounds of my Ultimatum, where emotions dictate reality.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002670_METEION<tab>Vous franchissez la frontière de notre nid. Ici, les sentiments l'emportent sur la réalité.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002680_METEION<tab>Where resignation and acceptance unite to embrace the end.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002680_METEION<tab>Et les émotions qui étreignent vos cœurs ne leur permettent plus de battre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002690_METEION<tab>Where those who yet valiantly cling to life cannot thrive...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002690_METEION<tab>Respirer<var 1D /var>? Ici, vous ne sauriez même pas exister.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002700_ESTINIEN<tab>By the Fury...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002700_ESTINIEN<tab>Argh... Qu'est-ce qui vient de nous arriver<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002710_URIANGER<tab>Thancred...?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002710_URIANGER<tab>Où est Thancred...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002720_YSHTOLA<tab>Meteion is gone as well. Mayhap he awakened first and gave chase.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002720_YSHTOLA<tab>Il s'est peut-être lancé à la poursuite de Météion. Elle a disparu, elle aussi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002730_MAPPINGWAY<tab>...Uh, everyone? It appears we're at our destination.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002730_MAPPINGWAY<tab>Bah ça... Je sais pas comment on s'est débrouillé, mais on a atterri.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002740_MAPPINGWAY<tab>This...this is Ultima Thule.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002740_MAPPINGWAY<tab>Nous sommes arrivés à Ultima Thulé.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002750_GROWINGWAY<tab>Not that we knew what to expect...but I wasn't expecting this.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002750_GROWINGWAY<tab>C'est pas tout... Je détecte des con<var 16 /var>struc<var 16 /var>tions dehors, et même une atmosphère<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002760_GROWINGWAY<tab>From atmospheric composition to ambient temperatures, all readings are within permissible range. This place is capable of supporting life!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002760_GROWINGWAY<tab>Composition... température... luminosité... Vous pourriez même sortir sans scaphandre<var 1D /var>! Alors qu'il devrait y avoir rien du tout ici<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002770_LIVINGWAY<tab>If that's the case, then Thancred may well have gone on ahead. Let's go and have a look.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002770_LIVINGWAY<tab>Thancred pourrait se trouver à l'extérieur, sortons pour vérifier. Je passerai devant.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002780_LIVINGWAY<tab>Meanwhile, I want the rest of you to perform a full inspection of the ship as well as a biological scan.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002780_LIVINGWAY<tab>En attendant notre retour, contrôlez les systèmes de A à Z. Je veux qu'on soit prêts à partir à tout moment. Et scannez l'intérieur du vaisseau à la recherche de signatures biologiques, on ne sait jamais.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_002790_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>So it was that the brave wayfarers arrived at last at dream's end.
