source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005490_ALPHINAUD<tab>But I can only imagine how heavy the weight would be this time.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005490_ALPHINAUD<tab>J'ai peur qu'ils te paraissent plus lourds quand nous ne serons plus là pour les porter avec toi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005500_ALPHINAUD<tab>As your friend, I cannot bear the thought of making you suffer so.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005500_ALPHINAUD<tab>Je m'en voudrais pour toujours d'avoir causé du tort à mon ami<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>... Et j'aimerais pouvoir éviter de t'infliger ça...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005510_ALISAIE<tab>Then why suggest such a thing!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005510_ALISAIE<tab>Eh ben on lui inflige pas, et puis c'est tout<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005520_ALISAIE<tab>It's too much to ask of anyone─even <var 08 E905 ((her)) ((him)) /var>!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005520_ALISAIE<tab>Moi non plus, je veux pas lui faire subir ça<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005530_ALISAIE<tab>Why must <var 08 E905 ((she)) ((he)) /var> be the one? Why must <var 08 E905 ((she)) ((he)) /var> fight alone?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005530_ALISAIE<tab>J'en ai marre qu'<var 08 E905 ((elle)) ((il)) /var> soit toujours obligé<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> de se battre tout<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> seul<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005540_ALISAIE<tab>More than a hero, <var 08 E905 ((she)) ((he)) /var>'s a dear friend.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005540_ALISAIE<tab>C'est bien plus que notre ami<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>, c'est notre <var 08 E905 ((héroïne)) ((héros)) /var>...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005550_ALISAIE<tab>Not only to us, but to so many others. There are so many people in the world who care for you, and yet...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005550_ALISAIE<tab>Et pas que <var 08 E905 ((la)) ((le)) /var> nôtre... Y a des gens qui l'adorent aux quatre coins du monde... Alors pourquoi il faut toujours que ça tombe sur <var 08 E905 ((elle)) ((lui)) /var><var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005560_ALISAIE<tab>And yet...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005560_ALISAIE<tab>Pourquoi, hein<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005570_ALISAIE<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005570_ALISAIE<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005580_ALPHINAUD<tab>Alisaie. I have an idea.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005580_ALPHINAUD<tab>Ne t'en fais pas, petite sœur... J'ai plus d'un tour dans mon sac.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005590_ALPHINAUD<tab>Given the nature of this realm, it may be possible to do more than unbar our friend's path. We might also pave <var 08 E905 ((her)) ((him)) /var> a new one.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005590_ALPHINAUD<tab>Nos sentiments prennent substance ici. Nous devrions donc pouvoir faire plus que lui ouvrir la voie.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005600_ALPHINAUD<tab>For instance...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005600_ALPHINAUD<tab>Il faut croire, toujours croire...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005610_ALPHINAUD<tab>A path where he finds happiness at journey's end.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005610_ALPHINAUD<tab>“Au bout de sa route, un dénouement heureux l'attend.”

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005620_ALPHINAUD<tab>A path where she finds happiness at journey's end.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005620_ALPHINAUD<tab>“Au bout de sa route, un dénouement heureux l'attend.”

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005630_ALPHINAUD<tab>This much, I think we can believe with the utmost conviction. No matter how deep our despair.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005630_ALPHINAUD<tab>Même au plus profond de l'abîme, on devrait pouvoir s'accrocher à cette pensée, toi et moi, non<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005640_ALPHINAUD<tab>So please, believe in us too. And press on.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005640_ALPHINAUD<tab>Tu nous fais confiance, pas vrai<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005650_ALPHINAUD<tab>Thank you...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005650_ALPHINAUD<tab>Je le savais...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005660_ALPHINAUD<tab>What are you─!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005660_ALPHINAUD<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005670_ALISAIE<tab>If the plan's decided, then let's not dally.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005670_ALISAIE<tab>On a notre plan, alors pas la peine de lambiner<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005680_METEION<tab>Ah, there you are. It was as I said, was it not?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005680_METEION<tab>Vous voyez<var 1D /var>? Je vous avais bien dit qu'il n'y avait plus personne.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005690_ALPHINAUD<tab>It was. We couldn't find anyone.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005690_ALPHINAUD<tab>Tu n'as pas menti, Météion. Il n'y avait pas âme qui vive.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005700_ALPHINAUD<tab>But this place isn't entirely deserted, is it? You are here.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005700_ALPHINAUD<tab>Si ce n'est toi, bien sûr...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005710_ALPHINAUD<tab>You sought out a star of promise and found a ruined husk.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005710_ALPHINAUD<tab>Tu as dit avoir trouvé cette planète déserte à ton arrivée.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005720_ALPHINAUD<tab>Like us, you explored the devastation. Like us, you were stricken.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005720_ALPHINAUD<tab>Et comme nous, tu as dû explorer ses ruines, un sentiment d'angoisse naissant pas après pas au creux de ton ventre, à mesure que tu t'interrogeais...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005730_ALPHINAUD<tab>Horrified by the thought that so many lives could be snuffed out as if they were worth nothing.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005730_ALPHINAUD<tab>Comment une civilisation pareille a-t-elle pu disparaître dans l'indifférence la plus totale<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005740_ALPHINAUD<tab>And the thought that you would have to bear the terrible tidings to Hermes.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005740_ALPHINAUD<tab>Comment annoncer la nouvelle à Hermès sans briser ses espoirs<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005750_ALPHINAUD<tab>That which you saw and felt, you shared with your sisters. As did they share their own grim findings with you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005750_ALPHINAUD<tab>D'autant plus que tes sœurs continuaient de t'envoyer leurs rapports, tous plus consternants les uns que les autres.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005760_ALPHINAUD<tab>Overcome by the pervasive despair of these stars, some of you inadvertently ushered their peoples to their ends.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005760_ALPHINAUD<tab>Certaines d'entre elles se lamentaient sur le sort d'astres dépeuplés... D'autres voyaient leur cœur s'imprégner du découragement de leurs habitants, et sans le vouloir, accéléraient leur disparition...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005770_ALPHINAUD<tab>Knowing the horrors you know, anyone would feel the same. They would fear what lies ahead, and struggle to move forward.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005770_ALPHINAUD<tab>Dans ces conditions, n'importe qui aurait peur d'avancer.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005780_METEION<tab>Fear... I had forgotten that such a thing existed, so focused have I been on shepherding despair.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005780_METEION<tab>C'est amusant, j'avais com<var 16 /var>plè<var 16 /var>te<var 16 /var>ment oublié ce sentiment... Le désespoir dont je me suis gorgée l'avait effacé...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005790_ALPHINAUD<tab>If you can remember, then you can still face and overcome your own fear.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005790_ALPHINAUD<tab>Tu peux encore faire marche arrière, Météion. Il te suffit de rappeler à ta mémoire l'angoisse que tu as ressentie... et de l'affronter...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005800_METEION<tab>Why would I bother with such an insignificant emotion? If the despair I command is as a raging river, then fear is but a trickling stream.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005800_METEION<tab>Impossible... Je ne suis plus qu'un torrent bouillonnant de haine pour la vie. Un fleuve inarrêtable qui charrie les vœux d'ané<var 16 /var>an<var 16 /var>tis<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment de ceux dans l'impasse.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005810_METEION<tab>It can do nothing to alter my flow.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005810_METEION<tab>L'angoisse ou la peur que j'ai pu ressentir autrefois ne sont rien à côté. Elles sont emportées par les flots qui me traversent, et noyées dans leurs courants.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005820_METEION<tab>You spoke with the Ea, yes? Heard their tale of what awaits the universe?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005820_METEION<tab>Les Éas... Ils vous ont parlé de la fin de l'univers, n'est-ce pas<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005830_METEION<tab>It's true. The stars grow colder and more distant. Eventually all will enjoy frozen solitude.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005830_METEION<tab>Ils ont raison, vous savez. Les astres s'éloignent les uns des autres. L'espace ne sera bientôt plus qu'un vide gelé.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005840_METEION<tab>Using the power of dynamis, I am hastening that process.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005840_METEION<tab>J'accélère même le processus en me servant du dynamis.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005850_METEION<tab>In so doing, nothing will be born ever again. Everyone will remain dead.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005850_METEION<tab>C'est mieux, vous ne croyez pas<var 1D /var>? Comme ça, la vie ne renaîtra jamais, et la douleur non plus.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005860_METEION<tab>Alas, it will take time for that to happen. So in mercy I sent you my gift, to spare you needless suffering.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005860_METEION<tab>Mal<var 16 /var>heu<var 16 /var>reu<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment, ça n'arrivera pas tout de suite. Et moi, je ne veux pas vous voir souffrir inutilement. Alors j'offre une alternative plus rapide à toutes les civilisations qui subsistent encore<var 1D /var>: l'ané<var 16 /var>an<var 16 /var>tis<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005870_METEION<tab>Don't worry. Even if no living witnesses remain to mark the event, I'll make certain that Etheirys has a proper end.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005870_METEION<tab>Ne craignez rien. La vie cessera sur Ætherys, et personne ne verra ce que vous y avez accompli, mais je vous promets que cette tragédie ne se reproduira plus.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005880_ALISAIE<tab>For all the power you wield, you're more fearful than the familiar you used to be.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005880_ALISAIE<tab>Je me rends compte... Les pouvoirs que tu as acquis dépassent l'entendement. Et pourtant, tu te laisses plus que jamais guider par la peur.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005890_ALISAIE<tab>That Meteion feared simply to move forward, but your fear is such that you've given up on everything.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005890_ALISAIE<tab>Je me trompe<var 1D /var>? Autrefois, tu craignais peut-être d'avancer, comme Alphinaud l'a dit, mais aujourd'hui, tu as tellement peur de tout que tu te complais dans l'abandon.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005900_ALISAIE<tab>I know it well. That sense of defeat. I've tasted my fair share of it.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005900_ALISAIE<tab>Je te comprends, tu sais<var 1D /var>!? Ça nous est arrivé plein de fois aussi<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005910_ALISAIE<tab>But as many times as we've fallen down, we've learned how to pick ourselves up and carry on.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005910_ALISAIE<tab>La différence... C'est que nous on a appris comment se relever après avoir trébuché, même quand on se heurte à une difficulté insurmontable.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005920_ALISAIE<tab>We take each other's hand. Share in each other's courage. Follow in each other's footsteps. And turn sorrow into strength!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005920_ALISAIE<tab>On saisit toutes les mains tendues, on emprunte du courage chaque fois qu'il nous est offert... On poursuit nos idéaux en tirant force de notre dépit<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005930_ALPHINAUD<tab>There are times when we fail. We bear wounds that do not heal.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005930_ALPHINAUD<tab>Et même ainsi, il nous est arrivé d'échouer, de subir des blessures qui ne pourront jamais entièrement se refermer<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005940_ALPHINAUD<tab>But these experiences are part of life, and they make us stronger!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005940_ALPHINAUD<tab>Mais elles, comme le reste, nous rappellent le chemin parcouru<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005950_ALPHINAUD<tab>(-Alphinaud and Alisaie-)We rise, fall, and rise again!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005950_ALPHINAUD<tab>(-Alphinaud et Alisaie-)Et c'est pour ça que nous continuerons toujours à aller de l'avant<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005960_ALISAIE<tab>We rise, fall, and rise again!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005960_ALISAIE<tab>Et c'est pour ça que nous continuerons toujours à aller de l'avant<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005970_ALISAIE<tab>Don't worry about us. You must take the next step, and all the rest after that.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005970_ALISAIE<tab>T'en fais pas, ça va aller<var 1D /var>! T'occupe pas de nous, et continue à avancer... un pied devant l'autre<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005975_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>Earlier, in Old Sharlayan...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005975_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>Un peu plus tôt

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005980_TATARU<tab>Please... Please... Oh, please let them all be safe...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005980_TATARU<tab>Faites qu'ils s'en sortent... Faites qu'ils s'en sortent...<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005990_KRILE<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_005990_KRILE<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006000_TATARU<tab>Krile? Are you all right?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006000_TATARU<tab>Krile...<var 1D /var>? Tu te sens mal...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006010_KRILE<tab>It's nothing... Just a headache.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006010_KRILE<tab>C'est rien, Tataru. Juste un petit mal de tête.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006020_KRILE<tab>They'll be fine... I know they will...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006020_KRILE<tab>Tout va bien... Jusqu'ici, tout va bien...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006030_IMMIGRATIONCONTROLSTAFF<tab>Apologies for the interruption! A man arrived on the last ferry. An associate of the Scions!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006030_IMMIGRATIONCONTROLSTAFF<tab>E-excusez-moi de vous déranger dans un moment pareil<var 1D /var>! Un navire vient d'accoster avec une personne importante à son bord<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006040_IMMIGRATIONCONTROLSTAFF<tab>He wishes to speak with you at once!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006040_IMMIGRATIONCONTROLSTAFF<tab>Elle... Elle demande audience auprès des Héritiers de la Septième Aube<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006050_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>In this city devoid of life, you sense the presence of another...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006050_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>Vous ressentez maintenant des présences dans la Cité silencieuse...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006060_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>The sorrow of a thousand thousand worlds weighs heavy. And yet you can walk on.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006060_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>Le fardeau de désespoir de tous ces mondes pèse désormais sur vous seul<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>, mais vous vous sentez encore la force de mettre un pied devant l'autre...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006070_METEION<tab>Here the path ends. There is no way to reach our nest.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006070_METEION<tab>Aucun chemin ne mène au cœur de notre nid. Te voilà incapable d'aller de l'avant, maintenant.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006080_METEION<tab>I told you. Resignation and acceptance reign in this place.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006080_METEION<tab>Je te l'ai pourtant dit. Les émotions qui tourbillonnent ici rejettent la vie.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006090_METEION<tab>The rejection of life by those who came to curse it.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006090_METEION<tab>Vous persévérez, vous vous accrochez tant bien que mal, mais dans les derniers instants, vous maudissez immanquablement votre sort.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006100_METEION<tab>Those whose dreams were unfulfilled. Whose prayers were unheard. Whose labors were unrewarded.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006100_METEION<tab>Mes vœux n'ont pas été exaucés... Personne n'a entendu mes prières... Mes efforts n'auront jamais porté leurs fruits...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006110_METEION<tab>Hope cannot deliver you unto hopelessness. Our refuge is beyond you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006110_METEION<tab>Tous ces sentiments affluent et se concentrent ici. Il n'y a plus de place pour la moindre espérance.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006120_METEION<tab>Always has it been. Such is the nature of this place.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006120_METEION<tab>Les différents chemins sur lesquels vous vous engagez se terminent tous par une impasse, tu comprends<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006130_METEION<tab>You should have remained on Etheirys.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006130_METEION<tab>Voilà pourquoi j'aurais préféré que vous attendiez sagement votre heure sur Ætherys...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006140_METEION<tab>Struggle will avail you naught, nor will it grant your comrades peace.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006140_METEION<tab>Tu commences à comprendre que vos efforts sont futiles et que tu ne peux rien y faire. Obstine-toi à rester ici, et tes amis ne trouveront jamais le repos.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006150_METEION<tab>Come, let me relieve you of your burden. You have suffered enough.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006150_METEION<tab>Abandonne cette souffrance, oublie-la. Face à elle, que peux-tu espérer d'autre que la délivrance de toute façon<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006155_ALL<tab>[MYRIAD VOICES] REPORT IF DISPLAYED
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006155_ALL<tab>（大勢の声出力用ラベル・翻訳不要）

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006160_YSHTOLA<tab>Azem's magick. So long as our souls remain, you can use it to summon us back. But you mustn't.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006160_YSHTOLA<tab>Le cristal d'Azem a reçu la bénédiction d'Hydaelyn. Il devrait pouvoir nous ramener, tant qu'une partie de notre âme subsiste.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006170_THANCRED<tab>That's why...it's too soon for this to end.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006170_THANCRED<tab>C'est bien pour ça qu'on ne peut pas la laisser disparaître comme ça...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006180_KRILE<tab>You must triumph.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006180_KRILE<tab>Triomphez.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006190_BLOEWYDA<tab>Be safe, all of you. And come back.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006190_BLOEWYDA<tab>Revenez-nous sains et saufs, d'accord<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006200_AMON<tab>After all these years...is this the answer I was hoping for?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006200_AMON<tab>Qu'est-ce que j'attendais depuis toujours...<var 1D /var>? La réponse que j'espérais au fond de moi, et que je n'ai jamais eue...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006210_VENAS<tab>So long as we remember, our fates remain ours to shape.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006210_VENAS<tab>Rien n'est encore perdu. Il nous reste des cartes à jouer.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006220_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>Perhaps when our time comes to return to the star, we shall remember these few days we have lost.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006220_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>Peut-être... que lorsque ce sera notre tour, on finira par se rappeler cette parenthèse oubliée<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006230_EMETSELCH<tab>Do not squander it. The legacy I leave you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006230_EMETSELCH<tab>Ce que mon moi futur t'a légué... Ne le perds pas.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q10_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q10_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que dites-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A10_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>I won't forsake our cause.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A10_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Jamais je n'oublierai<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A10_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>I'll reach you! I'll find a way!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A10_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Je surmonterai toutes les impasses<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006240_EMETSELCH<tab>(-???-)I bid them remember, but all this time, <var 1A 02 /var>I'm<var 1A 01 /var> the one who had forgotten... A right fool you've made of me, Hermes.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006240_EMETSELCH<tab>(-???-)Tss... Je lui demande de se souvenir de nous, et c'est nous qui l'avions oublié<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> tout ce temps... Hermès nous aura bien fait tourner en bourrique<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006250_EMETSELCH<tab>(-???-)And to add insult to injury, I've been denied a sound rest, forced to watch this clamorous show.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006250_EMETSELCH<tab>(-???-)Moi qui pensais que j'allais pouvoir profiter d'un repos bien mérité. Au lieu de ça, je me retrouve à suivre les aventures de <var 08 E905 ((cette fâcheuse)) ((ce fâcheux)) /var>.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006260_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>(-???-)Oh come now, it's been a gripping tale. Unbreakable bonds and noble sacrifice, sprinkled with moments of levity to counterbalance the pathos. It's got it all.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006260_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>(-???-)Allons, allons, elles ont le mérite d'être trépidantes. Avoue <var 08 E905 ((qu'elle)) ((que lui)) /var> et ses amis nous ont époustouflés<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006270_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>(-???-)I for one would have been perfectly content to watch enraptured from the stalls...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006270_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>(-???-)Ç'aurait été bête de partir avant la fin du spectacle, non<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006280_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>But I won't say no to a bit part!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006280_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>Heureux que tu aies fait appel à nous<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006290_METEION<tab>What are you?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006290_METEION<tab>Qui êtes-vous<var 1D /var>? Je ne vous connais pas...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006300_EMETSELCH<tab>Half-faded souls of the dead. Isn't it painfully obvious?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006300_EMETSELCH<tab>Des fantômes à demi effacés, merci de nous le rappeler.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006310_EMETSELCH<tab>Worry not─we haven't the power to defeat you. Nor is it our duty to do so. Not anymore.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006310_EMETSELCH<tab>Ne crains rien, je n'ai pas la force de te nuire. Et puis, je dois laisser la vedette à <var 08 E905 ((celle)) ((celui)) /var> qui m'a vaincu.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006320_EMETSELCH<tab>That being said, we do have a score to settle.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006320_EMETSELCH<tab>Cela dit... J'attendais avec impatience nos retrouvailles. Nous avons des comptes à régler, toi et moi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006330_EMETSELCH<tab>So, here I am, Venat. I suppose you needed me to tie it all together, these frayed threads of our history─but knowing you, I suspect there's a joke in it too. Oh yes, I can imagine you gloating over my forgetfulness.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006330_EMETSELCH<tab>Venat a toujours eu trop de suite dans les idées. M'aurait-elle épargné pour faire de moi la clef de voûte de son pont à travers les âges<var 1D /var>? À moins que ce ne soit un reproche voilé, ma punition pour avoir oublié bien malgré moi la cause de l'apocalypse...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006340_EMETSELCH<tab>Were I feeling charitable, I might assume you had left room for the possibility of this outcome.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006340_EMETSELCH<tab>Quoique, si je n'étais pas mauvaise langue, je dirais qu'elle a simplement cherché à orchestrer cet ultime coup de théâtre...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006350_EMETSELCH<tab>Even so, you'll get no applause from me. A single gesture will not lighten the burden I've had to bear.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006350_EMETSELCH<tab> Si elle s'attend à des re<var 16 /var>mer<var 16 /var>cie<var 16 /var>ments, elle sera bien mal servie. Ma vie ne fut pas un long fleuve tranquille, et ce revirement de cœur n'y changera rien.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006360_EMETSELCH<tab>Still, you must be commended. Our methods would not have brought mankind this far.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006360_EMETSELCH<tab>Je dois néanmoins lui reconnaître un certain don d'entremetteuse. Ce n'est pas avec nos méthodes qu'un être humain serait parvenu à mettre les pieds ici.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006370_EMETSELCH<tab>And so, as a show of respect to the last of us, I make this declaration.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006370_EMETSELCH<tab>Soit. En guise d'éloges à Venat, et d'ultime offrande à l'humanité originelle, je peux bien me fendre d'un préambule<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006380_EMETSELCH<tab>You will not end our journey!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006380_EMETSELCH<tab>Chantre de l'ané<var 16 /var>an<var 16 /var>tis<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment, nous ne serons pas défaits par tes vœux funestes<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006390_EMETSELCH<tab>That is our answer! The answer of all lives of Etheirys, past and present!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006390_EMETSELCH<tab>Telle est la parole des peuples de jadis et d'aujourd'hui<var 1D /var>! La réponse qu'ils t'opposent en chœur<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006400_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>As you've called us to the stage, so shall we perform. And creation magicks never fail to please.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006400_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>Tu as eu la gentillesse de nous inviter. Permets-nous de te rendre la pareille avec un brin de magie créatrice.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006410_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>Drawing upon the hopes of your comrades, we will make for you a new path.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006410_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>Les sentiments de tes amis imprègnent l'air qui nous entoure... Nous allons nous en servir, les filer un à un afin de tisser le sort qui t'ouvrira la voie.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006420_EMETSELCH<tab>What form said path takes depends on you. So focus─focus and envision that which rejects the claim that you cannot attain your goal!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006420_EMETSELCH<tab>Son aspect ne dépendra que de toi. Choisis celui qui te permettra de la toucher en plein cœur, celui qui te permettra d'avancer<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006430_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>Ours is the wisdom to weave the fabric of reality...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006430_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>L'entrelacs de nos savoirs... forme la trame de l'astre à l'aube des âges...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006440_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>Ours is the power to create!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006440_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>Le pouvoir de la création entre nos mains... nous façonnons la réalité<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006450_HERMES<tab>Meteion.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006450_HERMES<tab>Météion...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006460_HERMES<tab>Though I gave you these wings to soar the heavens, I did not teach you how to walk the earth. So loath was I to bind another living being.
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006460_HERMES<tab>Je t'ai peut-être appris à voler, mais je n'ai pas été en mesure de t'enseigner comment vivre<var 1D /var>;
comment trouver ta place dans cet immense univers en tant qu'être unique.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006470_HERMES<tab>In the course of your long journey, you will learn from those you meet. Learn to walk and run and so much more.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006470_HERMES<tab>Malgré tout, j'ai bon espoir qu'au bout de ton long périple se trouvera quelqu'un qui saura enfin combler cette lacune.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006480_HERMES<tab>A flower.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006480_HERMES<tab>Des fleurs.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006490_HERMES<tab>Yes. Upon your return, I will gift you a beautiful flower.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006490_HERMES<tab>Si tu accomplis ton voyage jusqu'au bout, je t'offrirai des fleurs qui symboliseront toute mon affection.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006500_EMETSELCH<tab>These Elpis blooms serve as proof that this realm is not utterly devoid of hope. No more can you deny its power. No more is yours the dominion of despair.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006500_EMETSELCH<tab>Ces elpis témoignent de la présence immuable du sentiment qui les a fait fleurir. Aussi longtemps que ce champ recouvrira cet astre, le désespoir ne pourra plus régner sans partage en ces lieux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006510_EMETSELCH<tab>In case the practical implications were lost on you, your comrades no longer need fight their fight.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006510_EMETSELCH<tab>Cela signifie une chose<var 1D /var>: que les âmes de tes amis n'ont plus besoin de se battre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006520_EMETSELCH<tab>So, go on. Call them back to your side.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006520_EMETSELCH<tab>Rappelle-les, et ensemble, continuez d'avancer.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006530_HYDAELYN<tab>May you ever walk...in the light...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006530_HYDAELYN<tab>Puissent-ils veiller sur toi...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006540_THANCRED<tab>How disappointing. Not even a single scar in the making to brag about.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006540_THANCRED<tab>Hmpf. Et moi qui m'attendais à une ou deux balafres pour pouvoir me vanter...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006550_ESTINIEN<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006550_ESTINIEN<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006560_ESTINIEN<tab>You'll find a way regardless.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006560_ESTINIEN<tab>Tu ne vas pas te plaindre quand même<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006570_YSHTOLA<tab>Honestly... This is far more than any of us could have hoped for. Let us be thankful.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006570_YSHTOLA<tab>Franchement... On s'en sort sans une égratignure. Il y a de quoi être content.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006580_URIANGER<tab>Indeed. That we thus stand reunited is a gift. Let us not squander it, and see that we all return to Etheirys.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006580_URIANGER<tab>Nous pourrons rentrer tous ensemble sur Ætherys... Là où tous nos amis nous attendent.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006590_GRAHATIA<tab>Aye, as soon as we've averted the Final Days!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006590_GRAHATIA<tab>On a juste une petite apocalypse à stopper avant ça<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006600_ALISAIE<tab>Good to see you again. Our heroic sacrifice paid off, I take it?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006600_ALISAIE<tab>On s'est débrouillés comme des chefs, tu crois pas<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006610_ALPHINAUD<tab>Come, my friends. Let us carry on and finish it─together.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006610_ALPHINAUD<tab>Il est temps de conclure cette aventure. Allons-y, et tous ensemble cette fois<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q11_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q11_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que dites-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A11_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>It's over, Meteion.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A11_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Ton voyage s'achève enfin.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A11_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Come with us, Meteion.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A11_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Viens, Météion. Rentrons à la maison.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006620_METEION<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006620_METEION<tab><var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006630_METEION<tab>Can you...hear me...?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006630_METEION<tab>Est-ce... Est-ce que vous... m'entendez...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006640_METEION<tab>The voices within... Crying in pain, wailing in sorrow... Hurting... Hurting...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006640_METEION<tab>L-leurs sentiments... Ils se sont fondus en moi... Je les entends... Leur chagrin... Leur peine...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006650_METEION<tab>End it...silence it... Silence our song of oblivion!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006650_METEION<tab>S'il vous plaît... M-mettez fin... à tout ça...<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006660_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>The way is open. They can proceed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006660_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>La voie est ouverte... Ils n'ont plus qu'à arpenter le chemin, maintenant...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006670_EMETSELCH<tab>So it seems.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006670_EMETSELCH<tab>Comme nous tous...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006680_ALISAIE<tab>You're leaving!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006680_ALISAIE<tab>Quoi<var 1D /var>!? Vous retournez dans la mer des étoiles<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006690_EMETSELCH<tab>Of course. The encore is finished, and I will not suffer myself to live again by Hydaelyn's magick.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006690_EMETSELCH<tab>Évidemment. Nous n'avons jamais demandé à être ressuscités grâce au pouvoir d'Hydaelyn.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006700_EMETSELCH<tab>But more than that, the future you seek is not the past we loved. That is why we fought. And why I lost.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006700_EMETSELCH<tab>Les lendemains que vous poursuivez ne sont en rien comparables au passé que je chérissais. C'est d'ailleurs de ce clivage qu'ont découlé notre af<var 16 /var>fron<var 16 /var>te<var 16 /var>ment et ses con<var 16 /var>sé<var 16 /var>quen<var 16 /var>ces.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006710_EMETSELCH<tab>But though you defeated me, my ideals are inviolate. Invincible.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006710_EMETSELCH<tab>Vous m'avez vaincu, mais mes idéaux, eux, sont invincibles. Et même dans la défaite, je m'assurerai qu'ils le restent.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006720_EMETSELCH<tab>Spare me your pity. I have no use for it. If you would do something for me─save our star.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006720_EMETSELCH<tab>Gardez votre compassion. Seule l'éradication du mal qui nous empoisonne doit occuper vos pensées. Sans cela, vous n'aurez pas la détermination nécessaire pour triompher.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006730_EMETSELCH<tab>See this tale to a triumphant conclusion, and with elation in your hearts, bid the final curtain fall.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006730_EMETSELCH<tab>Et lorsque vos hourras auront supplanté vos cris de guerre, que l'émotion sera à son comble, seulement là, pourrez-vous faire tomber le rideau.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006740_EMETSELCH<tab>Only then may it rise again and a new tale begin─with new parts for all to play.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006740_EMETSELCH<tab>La prochaine pièce pourra se jouer. Sur une nouvelle scène et avec de nouveaux rôles, pour vous comme pour nous.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006750_EMETSELCH<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006750_EMETSELCH<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006760_EMETSELCH<tab>Tell me, have you been to the ruins beneath the waters of the Bounty?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006760_EMETSELCH<tab>As-tu déjà exploré les ruines qui dorment au fin fond de la mer de l'Abondance<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006770_EMETSELCH<tab>Or the treasure islands beyond the frozen waters of Blindfrost, in Othard's north?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006770_EMETSELCH<tab>As-tu déjà voyagé au nord d'Othard<var 1D /var>? Où la vue des côtes de l'île au trésor ne s'offre qu'aux intrépides assez fous pour franchir la mer gelée.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006780_EMETSELCH<tab>The fabled golden cities of the New World? The sacred sites of the forgotten people of the south sea isles?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006780_EMETSELCH<tab>As-tu déjà contemplé l'éclat des cités d'or du nouveau continent<var 1D /var>? Les statues des saints enfants sculptées par les oubliés des îles méridionales<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006790_EMETSELCH<tab>What about Meracydia, the southern continent? Do you know aught of its present state of affairs?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006790_EMETSELCH<tab>Sais-tu comment se porte Méracydia, si longtemps après avoir été dévasté par Allag<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006800_EMETSELCH<tab>...I thought not. Even of your little Eorzea, you know precious little. The true identities of the Twelve, for instance.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006800_EMETSELCH<tab>Même en Éorzéa, tu as encore tant à découvrir. À commencer par la vérité sur ces fameux Douze. Quelle est leur origine<var 1D /var>? Te l'es-tu déjà demandé<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006810_EMETSELCH<tab>All of which is to say: expand your horizons. Go forth and seek discovery. Some of the civilizations in the reflections will surprise you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006810_EMETSELCH<tab>Et si ça ne te suffit toujours pas, tu n'as qu'à élargir tes horizons. Certains reflets abritent des civilisations si prospères qu'elles dépassent ton imagination.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006820_EMETSELCH<tab>As the bearer of Azem's crystal, you may consider your duty to see at least that much.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006820_EMETSELCH<tab>Tu possèdes le cristal d'Azem. Alors fais-lui honneur, et admire tous ces paysages.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006830_EMETSELCH<tab>I certainly did.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006830_EMETSELCH<tab>Je te garantis qu'ils valent le détour.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006840_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006840_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006850_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>I pray we meet again. If not in this life, then perhaps another.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006850_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>En espérant nous revoir un jour dans une autre vie, mon ami<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006860_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>Whensoever it should be, I trust it will be a most joyous reunion.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006860_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>Peut-être pas sous les mêmes traits, mais toujours tous les trois ensemble et dans la bonne humeur.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006870_EMETSELCH<tab>For you, maybe. I want nothing to do with it.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006870_EMETSELCH<tab>Très peu pour moi, merci.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006880_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>Oh, don't be that way.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006880_HYTHLODAEUS<tab>Ha, rabat-joie.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006890_METEION<tab>So you are finally here. In this place between death and rebirth, where life knows no dawn.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006890_METEION<tab>Alors, vous avez franchi le seuil... Vous pénétrez dans l'antichambre des âmes, entre la vie et la mort.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006900_METEION<tab>Come, then. Follow me down into the darkest depths of despair.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006900_METEION<tab>Allez, venez. Je vous invite au plus profond de mon nid... Laissez-vous emporter...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006910_METEION<tab>That you still stand... Your determination defies all reason.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006910_METEION<tab>Encore là... Seuls les inconscients manifestent un tel degré de détermination.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006920_METEION<tab>The souls within me writhe and recoil in your presence...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006920_METEION<tab>Mon cœur tremble à chacun de vos pas, comme si les civilisations qui l'ont marqué au fer rouge voyaient votre avancée d'un mauvais œil.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006930_METEION<tab>What must I do? What pain must I visit upon you to make you surrender to despair?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006930_METEION<tab>Comment vous convaincre de vous abandonner au désespoir, de nous rejoindre<var 1D /var>? Dites-moi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006940_ALISAIE<tab>No one is unbreakable. What pains one may weather may bring another to tears.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006940_ALISAIE<tab>Nous aussi, on souffre, comme tout le monde. Mais chacun endure une douleur qui est différente de toutes les autres.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006950_ALISAIE<tab>But therein lies our strength, for when we fall, our brothers and sisters are there to raise us up. Again and again. Without end.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006950_ALISAIE<tab>Voilà pourquoi même si l'un de nous trébuche, il trouvera toujours une main tendue pour l'aider à se relever, autant de fois qu'il le faut<var 1D /var>! Et jusqu'à ce qu'on repousse ton apocalypse<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006960_METEION<tab>I see...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006960_METEION<tab>En effet...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006970_METEION<tab>But no matter how much hope exists, ever will there be more despair.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006970_METEION<tab>Mais pour chaque espoir retrouvé, un nouveau malheur point à l'horizon.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006980_EAA<tab>But no matter how much hope exists, ever will there be more despair.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006980_EAA<tab>Mais pour chaque espoir retrouvé, un nouveau malheur point à l'horizon.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006990_EAB<tab>But no matter how much hope exists, ever will there be more despair.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_006990_EAB<tab>Mais pour chaque espoir retrouvé, un nouveau malheur point à l'horizon.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007000_MASTERSTIGMAONE<tab>But no matter how much hope exists, ever will there be more despair.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007000_MASTERSTIGMAONE<tab>Mais pour chaque espoir retrouvé, un nouveau malheur point à l'horizon.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007010_METEION<tab>Ever will the living curse the present and lament the future.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007010_METEION<tab>Les vivants portent le deuil du présent tout en craignant l'avenir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007020_EAA<tab>Ever will the living curse the present and lament the future.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007020_EAA<tab>Les vivants portent le deuil du présent tout en craignant l'avenir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007030_EAB<tab>Ever will the living curse the present and lament the future.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007030_EAB<tab>Les vivants portent le deuil du présent tout en craignant l'avenir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007040_MASTERSTIGMAONE<tab>Ever will the living curse the present and lament the future.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007040_MASTERSTIGMAONE<tab>Les vivants portent le deuil du présent tout en craignant l'avenir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007050_METEION<tab>So shall we sing until life ceases to be.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007050_METEION<tab>De leur premier, jusqu'à leur dernier souffle.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007060_EAA<tab>So shall we sing until life ceases to be.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007060_EAA<tab>De leur premier, jusqu'à leur dernier souffle.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007070_EAB<tab>So shall we sing until life ceases to be.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007070_EAB<tab>De leur premier, jusqu'à leur dernier souffle.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007080_MASTERSTIGMAONE<tab>So shall we sing until life ceases to be.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007080_MASTERSTIGMAONE<tab>De leur premier, jusqu'à leur dernier souffle.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007090_ALPHINAUD<tab>Seven hells!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007090_ALPHINAUD<tab>Qu'est-ce que c'est que ça<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007100_ESTINIEN<tab>On your guard!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007100_ESTINIEN<tab>En garde, camarades<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007110_ENDSINGER<tab>Ahhh, the rage... It rises... Rises...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007110_ENDSINGER<tab>Ah... Cette chaleur... Le feu ardent de la colère...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007120_ESTINIEN<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007120_ESTINIEN<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007130_METEION<tab>Stop!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007130_METEION<tab>(-???-)Stop<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007140_METEION<tab>Calm yourself. Please...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007140_METEION<tab>Je t'en prie, arrête<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007150_THANCRED<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007150_THANCRED<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007160_YSHTOLA<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007160_YSHTOLA<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007170_ENDSINGER<tab>We die in pain. We die in suffering! Who are you to live? Who are you to hope!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007170_ENDSINGER<tab>Pourquoi êtes-vous les seuls à vivre dans l'insouciance<var 1D /var>? Alors que nous avons souffert jusqu'à la fin<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007180_URIANGER<tab>Hold on, my friends!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007180_URIANGER<tab>Maintenant<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007190_ALPHINAUD<tab>Urianger, watch out!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007190_ALPHINAUD<tab>Urianger<var 1D /var>! Au-dessus de toi<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007200_URIANGER<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007200_URIANGER<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007210_ALPHINAUD<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007210_ALPHINAUD<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007220_URIANGER<tab>Alphinaud!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007220_URIANGER<tab>Alphinaud<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007230_ENDSINGER<tab>We cannot comprehend. We cannot know. We cannot know!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007230_ENDSINGER<tab>Rien ne saurait égaler la désolation qui nous accable... Comment osez-vous scander des mots d'espoir devant nous<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007240_METEION<tab>Don't, please! Don't do this to them. To yourself!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007240_METEION<tab>Ne leur fais pas de mal<var 1D /var>! Je t'en supplie... Tu ne feras que t'infliger plus de peine<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007250_ALISAIE<tab>Just one good strike.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007250_ALISAIE<tab>En espérant que ça passe<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007260_ALISAIE<tab>What!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007260_ALISAIE<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007270_ALISAIE<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007270_ALISAIE<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007280_METEION<tab>Stop. Please, stop!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007280_METEION<tab>S'il te plaît... Arrête<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007290_ENDSINGER<tab>We will not suffer alone...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007290_ENDSINGER<tab>Nous ne serons pas les seules à connaître le malheur...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007300_ENDSINGER<tab>All will know our pain!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007300_ENDSINGER<tab>Il se propagera, dans l'univers tout entier<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007310_GRAHATIA<tab>No you don't!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007310_GRAHATIA<tab>Pas si j'ai mon mot à dirrre<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007320_GRAHATIA<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007320_GRAHATIA<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007330_ENDSINGER<tab>All awash in ice. A frozen waste. Forever silent!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007330_ENDSINGER<tab>Tout va disparaître... La création se perdra dans un vide gelé et éternel<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007340_ALISAIE<tab>Wait!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007340_ALISAIE<tab>Attends<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007350_ALISAIE<tab>Don't!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007350_ALISAIE<tab>Non<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007360_ENDSINGER<tab>You gifted them escape.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007360_ENDSINGER<tab>Tu as permis à tes amis de s'échapper...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007370_ENDSINGER<tab>And rendered yourself powerless.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007370_ENDSINGER<tab>Quelle idée... Tu es désormais plus seul<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> que jamais.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007380_ENDSINGER<tab>Bereft of the synergy you claim is your strength. Unless you mean to call upon the dead once more.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007380_ENDSINGER<tab>Vous surmontez les difficultés en vous relevant les uns les autres. Maintenant que tu n'as plus de main à saisir, que vas-tu faire<var 1D /var>? Invoquer les disparus à nouveau<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007390_ENDSINGER<tab>Defiant to the last. But you will be one with us ere long.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007390_ENDSINGER<tab>Un ultime sursaut d'agonie<var 1D /var>? Parfait, nous ne ferons bientôt qu'un.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007400_ENDSINGER<tab>You will be battered and torn and made to crawl. You will weep and wail and curse your impotence. Curse your life as it fades.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007400_ENDSINGER<tab>Toi et les tiens rampez misérablement sur un bout de terre, déchirés et tiraillés de l'intérieur. Lorsque ta flamme vacillera pour la dernière fois, tu maudiras ton impuissance et les fondements de ce monde.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007410_ENDSINGER<tab>As we did! As we died!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007410_ENDSINGER<tab>Nous sommes passées par là. Ce n'est qu'une étape à franchir<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007420_ENDSINGER<tab>Such pain and sorrow we felt... Such anguish and rage... We tried. We tried. But it was no use...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007420_ENDSINGER<tab>En dépit de la peine, de la tristesse, de la misère, de la haine... nous avons tout fait pour nous raccrocher à la vie, en vain...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007430_ENDSINGER<tab>Only when we surrendered did we find release. Only when we embraced death.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007430_ENDSINGER<tab>Nous avons alors compris comment apporter un bonheur équitable à tous. En emportant le monde avec nous<var 1D /var>! La fin de tout<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007440_ENDSINGER<tab>So join us in despair...and embrace yours!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007440_ENDSINGER<tab>Viens<var 1D /var>! Rejoins-nous dans la plénitude du désespoir<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007450_ENDSINGER<tab>My Ultimatum... What is happening...?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007450_ENDSINGER<tab>Que se passe-t-il... Qui trouble la sérénité de notre nid...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007460_ZENOS<tab>At the end of everything I find you, my friend.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007460_ZENOS<tab>Enfin... Je te retrouve, mon ami<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007470_ZENOS<tab>I sought something in you, once. As you did in me.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007470_ZENOS<tab>J'ai la réponse à cette fameuse question. Je sais désormais ce que nous attendions l'un de l'autre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007480_ZENOS<tab>When at last I understood what it was, I journeyed to Sharlayan to seek you out. Struck a bargain with the woman who shares your gift.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007480_ZENOS<tab>J'ai donc traversé les mers pour venir te chercher, et conclu un marché avec cette fillette aux pouvoirs si singuliers.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007510_ZENOS<tab>In exchange for lending the Scions my aid, I was given the means to come hither.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007510_ZENOS<tab>J'ai promis de tendre la main aux Héritiers la prochaine fois qu'ils viendraient à plier le genou. En échange, elle m'a offert le moyen de te rejoindre ici.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007520_ZENOS<tab>Gorging upon what remained of the Mothercrystal, I reclaimed the form of the dragon. And hungry still for our reunion, I rode the light of the stars to you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007520_ZENOS<tab>J'ai dévoré ce qu'il restait du Cristal-mère, revêtu mon manteau d'écailles et traversé l'océan étoilé. Propulsé par le désir de t'affronter à nouveau, j'ai filé plus vite encore que la lumière.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007530_ZENOS<tab>I take it this is your prey.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007530_ZENOS<tab>Voilà donc la proie que tu traquais...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007550_ZENOS<tab>But why does it still live? Surely it is no match for you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007550_ZENOS<tab>Je ne comprends pas. Pourquoi vit-elle encore<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007560_ZENOS<tab>I had assumed you would be above something so banal as despair. Am I mistaken?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007560_ZENOS<tab>Tu m'as affirmé que ni le mal ni le désespoir ne sauraient t'ébranler. N'était-ce que de la vantardise<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q12_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q12_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que répondez-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A12_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>I don't want your help.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A12_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>N'espère pas une seconde que je vais te demander de l'aide.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A12_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>If it comes to it, I won't save you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A12_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Tu es le seul pour lequel je ne me battrai pas.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007570_ZENOS<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007570_ZENOS<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007580_ZENOS<tab>And I'd rather not give it. Nay, I would have preferred that we enjoy a private reunion.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007580_ZENOS<tab>À la bonne heure. C'est “contre” toi que je veux me battre. Nous allier ne ferait que diminuer mon appétit.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007590_ZENOS<tab>I care not. What I desire of you isn't succor. It is satisfaction.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007590_ZENOS<tab>Qu'importe. Tout ce que j'attends de toi, c'est que tu me montres tes crocs.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007600_ZENOS<tab>So come, let us dispense with this distraction, you and I!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007600_ZENOS<tab>Ma patience a ses limites... et cette chasse n'a que trop attendu<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007610_ENDSINGER<tab>You struggle in vain. You will not silence our song of oblivion!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007610_ENDSINGER<tab>Futile... Nous continuerons à appeler de nos vœux l'ané<var 16 /var>an<var 16 /var>tis<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment total<var 1D /var>! Ni vous ni personne ne pourra nous arrêter<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007620_ENDSINGER<tab>You will never reach it. Will never reach the deliverance you seek.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007620_ENDSINGER<tab>Mal<var 16 /var>heu<var 16 /var>reu<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment pour vous, l'issue que vous poursuivez sans relâche restera à jamais hors de votre portée...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007630_ENDSINGER<tab>If this...was not the answer...then what is it? Where lies...happiness...?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007630_ENDSINGER<tab>Comment...<var 1D /var>? Mais... je ne comprends pas... Si l'ané<var 16 /var>an<var 16 /var>tis<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment n'est pas la solution... Où le bonheur se cache-t-il...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007640_METEION<tab>No matter where we flew, there was only darkness and loneliness and pain.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007640_METEION<tab>J'ai volé le plus loin possible... Où que j'aille, je n'ai vu que l'obscurité, le froid, la solitude, la souffrance...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007650_METEION<tab>We couldn't find the answers Hermes yearned for. The answers he deserved.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007650_METEION<tab>Je n'ai pas pu trouver la réponse réconfortante qu'Hermès attendait...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007660_METEION<tab>Greetings... You who are my final encounter...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007660_METEION<tab>Bonjour... Tu seras la dernière personne que je rencontre...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007670_METEION<tab>I wish to hear your words... Share your feelings... Know your thoughts.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007670_METEION<tab>J'aimerais juste entendre ta voix... ressentir tes émotions... connaître tes pensées...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007680_METEION<tab>May we please...be friends?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007680_METEION<tab>Alors... tu veux bien être mon ami<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007690_METEION<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007690_METEION<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007700_METEION<tab>Yes, I can see them... The memories of a long, long journey...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007700_METEION<tab> Quel long voyage... Je vois tous ces souvenirs gravés dans ton cœur...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007710_METEION<tab>So many people... The thoughts of them overflowing in your heart...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007710_METEION<tab>Une myriade de rencontres... de destins croisés... de sentiments partagés... C'est donc ça...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007720_METEION<tab>What they live for, what gives their lives meaning... There was never a single answer.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007720_METEION<tab>Je comprends, maintenant... Le sens de la vie... Notre raison d'être... Il n'y avait pas de réponse unique à toutes ces questions...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007730_METEION<tab>You gather pieces of happiness, precious and fragile, only to lose them. Then start again.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007730_METEION<tab>Vous récoltez le bonheur petit à petit et sous bien des formes. Et même si le drame vient à frapper... vous reprenez sans cesse votre route, jour après jour.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007740_METEION<tab>On and on it goes, until death takes you into its gentle embrace.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007740_METEION<tab>Jusqu'à ce que la mort toque à votre porte, en voisine bien<var 16 /var>veil<var 16 /var>lan<var 16 /var>te.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007750_METEION<tab>That which Hermes sent us to find...was there all this time. On Etheirys.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007750_METEION<tab>Je n'avais pas besoin de voler si loin. La réponse à la question d'Hermès se trouvait sur notre planète depuis le début.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q13_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q13_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que dites-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A13_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>It wasn't always there.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A13_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Pas depuis le début, non.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A13_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>We created it together.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A13_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Chacun a d'abord dû apporter sa pierre à l'édifice.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007760_METEION<tab>Like a field of flowers, perhaps. At first a single blossom, it spreads and takes on more colors.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007760_METEION<tab>Un peu comme les fleurs d'un champ qui éclosent l'une après l'autre, jusqu'à former un océan multicolore s'étendant à perte de vue.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007770_METEION<tab>Thank you for guiding me here. To find these words at journey's end fills me with joy.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007770_METEION<tab>Je suis si heureuse de trouver enfin les mots... Merci... Je ne pouvais pas rêver plus belle conclusion à mon voyage...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007780_METEION<tab>And so, before I fall forever silent, there is one thing I must do.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007780_METEION<tab>Ça ne peut pas finir comme ça. Je dois amorcer un nouveau prélude avant de partir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007790_METEION<tab>No expression of regret will undo what my sisters and I have done. Will restore what we have stolen.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007790_METEION<tab>Je n'ai ni le pouvoir de restaurer ce que nous avons réduit à néant ni le droit d'implorer votre pardon.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007800_METEION<tab>But if you would allow it, I would sing one last song. A song of the newfound joy that swells in my heart...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007800_METEION<tab>En revanche, je voudrais chanter à nouveau... Célébrer la joie qui est parvenue à faire battre mon cœur.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007810_METEION<tab>Of the beauty of light when it shines across a dark and starless sea...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007810_METEION<tab>Je pourrais parler de la Lumière... de la beauté d'un rayon de soleil venant scinder les Ténèbres d'une nuit jusque là sans étoile.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007820_METEION<tab>Of a dream that from the soil of worlds now lost to sorrow, life will spring forth once more...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007820_METEION<tab>Ou adresser une prière, à ce grand vide froid... pour que la vie bourgeonne à nouveau, sur les terres abandonnées de civilisations disparues<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007830_METEION<tab>...Nourished by gentle rains and caressed by uplifting winds. A song of hope.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007830_METEION<tab>Une mélodie d'espoir, déversée à flots par les pluies battantes, portée au firmament par les vents tumultueux<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007840_METEION<tab>One day, life will fill the universe again. And Hermes will see this and smile.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007840_METEION<tab>J'espère qu'Hermès sera là pour le voir, lorsque la vie abondera.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007850_METEION<tab>How, I do not know. But I do know that, where there is a will, there is a way.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007850_METEION<tab>Je sais que ça parait impossible, mais j'ai confiance. Le dynamis est un océan de possibilités en perpétuel mouvement, et il tend toujours à concrétiser nos rêves.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007860_METEION<tab>After all, miracles happen every day, do they not?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007860_METEION<tab>Ça arrive bien parfois, les miracles, non<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007870_METEION<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007870_METEION<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007880_METEION<tab>I will create a path back to your ship, where your dear friends await.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007880_METEION<tab>Avant de nous quitter, je vais t'ouvrir la voie jusqu'au vaisseau où t'attendent tes amis.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007890_METEION<tab>Hold in your heart your desire to return to them, then follow my lead and walk forth.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007890_METEION<tab>Une fois que je serai partie, tu n'auras qu'à faire un pas, tout en souhaitant de tout ton cœur retourner auprès des tiens.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007900_METEION<tab>That hope will surely guide you true.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007900_METEION<tab>Ton vœu te guidera jusqu'à eux<var 1D /var>! Je te le promets<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007910_ZENOS<tab>You mean to return. To the world where you are hailed as a hero.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007910_ZENOS<tab>Que comptes-tu faire, maintenant<var 1D /var>? Rentrer dans ce monde qui t'a hissé<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> au rang <var 08 E905 ((d'héroïne)) ((de héros)) /var><var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007920_ZENOS<tab>Hear me then. Not as a hero, but as simply...you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007920_ZENOS<tab>Dans ce cas, c'est le moment ou jamais de nous mettre à nu.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007930_ZENOS<tab>As I learned in Ala Mhigo, you are a formidable foe.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007930_ZENOS<tab>J'ai réfléchi à notre ultime combat sur le toit du palais d'Ala Mhigo. À ce qui avait provoqué chez moi un tel sentiment d'allégresse.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007940_ZENOS<tab>Stronger than any I have faced. Against you, I need bring my all to bear.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007940_ZENOS<tab>Ce jour-là, j'ai affronté un<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> adversaire sans pareil. J'ai livré un duel m'obligeant à lutter jusqu'à mon dernier souffle.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007950_ZENOS<tab>I need burn through the candle of my life.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007950_ZENOS<tab>J'ai immolé ma vie, et elle a brillé plus intensément que jamais.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007960_ZENOS<tab>This is the sole pleasure I know, and it is the sole pleasure I have to share.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007960_ZENOS<tab>Il s'agit du plus grand bonheur que j'ai jamais ressenti, et de la plus belle offrande que je pourrai jamais te faire.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007970_ZENOS<tab>And so I come before you. To issue challenge and offer singular bliss.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007970_ZENOS<tab>J'attends donc de toi une revanche, ici et maintenant.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007980_ZENOS<tab>If you wish to walk away, I will not stop you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007980_ZENOS<tab>Libre à toi de refuser, et de retourner auprès des tiens. Je ne te retiendrai pas.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007990_ZENOS<tab>You value life. You do not burn yours save for reasons you deem worthy.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_007990_ZENOS<tab>Après tout, vous tenez la vie en estime. Et le bon sens semble vous dicter de la chérir et non de la mettre inutilement en danger.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008000_ZENOS<tab>Reasons such as those which brought you here. The salvation of a world and its people. The motives of a hero true.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008000_ZENOS<tab>Ce désir ardent de la protéger t'a d'ailleurs pro<var 16 /var>ba<var 16 /var>ble<var 16 /var>ment donné la force de parvenir jusqu'ici, aux confins des cieux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008010_ZENOS<tab>But there is more to you than that. You know this to be true.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008010_ZENOS<tab>Tu ne le réalises pas encore, mais ce lieu t'affranchit de toutes ces contraintes terrestres.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008020_ZENOS<tab>As surely as you know the thrill of pushing your body and soul to their limits. Of confronting ever-mightier foes, dancing ever closer to the precipice, wondering if this will be the one to finally, finally...fill the void.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008020_ZENOS<tab>Rappelle à ta mémoire l'euphorie enivrante de maîtriser enfin une nouvelle technique, la fièvre de découvrir une menace dépassant toutes les précédentes<var 1D /var>! Évoque tous ces souvenirs et laisse-les t'envahir<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008030_ZENOS<tab>Such pleasures, you seek for their own sake, and no other reason. Is this not so...<var 1A 02 /var>adventurer<var 1A 01 /var>?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008030_ZENOS<tab>On ne peut jouir de certains plaisirs qu'au péril de sa vie. Ose me contredire... <var 08 E905 ((aventurière)) ((aventurier)) /var>.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q14_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q14_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que répondez-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A14_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>That, I can't deny.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A14_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Tu as on ne peut plus raison.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A14_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Think what you will. But I'm not letting you leave this place.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A14_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Quoi qu'il en soit, tu ne repartiras pas d'ici vivant.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A14_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>I've had enough of you. It ends here.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A14_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>J'en ai assez de toi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008040_ZENOS<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008040_ZENOS<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008050_ZENOS<tab>Acceptance. At long last.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008050_ZENOS<tab>Commençons notre duel, alors.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008060_ZENOS<tab>The conflagration of our clash will scorch even the stars!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008060_ZENOS<tab>Brûlons ensemble... Que le brasier de nos vies rivalise avec celui des astres<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008070_ZENOS<tab>So you would still play the hero.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008070_ZENOS<tab>Tu resteras donc un symbole d'héroïsme jusqu'au bout...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008080_ZENOS<tab>No matter. In acceptance you betray your deception. You know full well what we are, and what we seek.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008080_ZENOS<tab>Qu'importe. Puisque tu relèves le défi, je révélerai cette facette de toi au cours de notre combat.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008090_ZENOS<tab>To shine incandescent in death's shadow!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008090_ZENOS<tab>Tu accepteras enfin ton goût immodéré pour le risque, et pour la joie frénétique qu'il procure<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008095_ZENOS<tab>Finally mustered the desire to kill me, have you?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008095_ZENOS<tab>Haaa... Voilà les crocs meurtriers que je souhaitais tant admirer.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008096_ZENOS<tab>Go on, then. Try and strike me down in this forsaken place. I shall return the favor.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008096_ZENOS<tab>Laisse donc mon cadavre pourrir au sein de cet abîme sans fin, si tu me vaincs. En échange, je ne retiendrai pas mes coups non plus.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008097_ZENOS<tab>Aye, let us indulge in the only worthwhile pursuit, and burn our lives to their ends!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008097_ZENOS<tab>Laissons l'extase du combat consumer nos vies<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008100_ZENOS<tab>Come, then!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008100_ZENOS<tab>Je t'attends<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008110_ZENOS<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008110_ZENOS<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008120_ZENOS<tab>That I should lose again...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008120_ZENOS<tab>Haaa... Encore une défaite...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008130_ZENOS<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008130_ZENOS<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008140_ZENOS<tab>How disappointing.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008140_ZENOS<tab>Quelle piètre performance...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008150_ZENOS<tab>Never have I understood those around me. Understood their obsessions.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008150_ZENOS<tab>Je n'ai jamais compris... comment les gens font pour accorder de la valeur à quoi que ce soit...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008160_ZENOS<tab>Besieged by their banality, the world was a mire of tedium and trivialities.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008160_ZENOS<tab>Une fange désolante... aussi hideuse qu'absurde... Voilà l'aspect qu'a toujours revêtu le monde à mes yeux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008170_ZENOS<tab>But in these fleeting moments, there is...a spark. Blinding, brilliant...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008170_ZENOS<tab>Certes, le soleil s'est levé en de rares occasions... pour balayer cette grisaille... et comme aujourd'hui, m'apporter un peu de gaieté...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008180_ZENOS<tab>Gone...too soon...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008180_ZENOS<tab>Mais dans l'ensemble... Tout m'a toujours paru exécrable...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008190_ZENOS<tab>What of you, my mirror? Born into this world, bestowed name, bid to seek out strife and adventure...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008190_ZENOS<tab>Et toi...<var 1D /var>? On t'a aussi donné un nom, lâché dans ce monde, et tu y as vécu...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008200_ZENOS<tab>Was this life a gift...or a burden?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008200_ZENOS<tab>Après avoir parcouru tout ce chemin... Qu'en penses-tu<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008210_ZENOS<tab>Did you find...fulfillment?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008210_ZENOS<tab>As-tu pu mordre dans la vie à pleine dents<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008220_ZENOS<tab>I...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008220_ZENOS<tab>Moi, je...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008230_ZENOS<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008230_ZENOS<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008240_ESTINIEN<tab>Can you hear... Say...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008240_ESTINIEN<tab>Hé, tu nous entends, camarade<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008250_URIANGER<tab>...must tend to...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008250_URIANGER<tab>Nous allons vous soigner tout de suite.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008260_GRAHATIA<tab>Open your... ...please!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008260_GRAHATIA<tab>Ouvrrre les yeux, je t'en prie<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008270_YSHTOLA<tab>Someone...hand...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008270_YSHTOLA<tab>Donnez-moi un coup de main<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008280_ALPHINAUD<tab>Please...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008280_ALPHINAUD<tab>Faites qu'<var 08 E905 ((elle)) ((il)) /var> s'en sorte<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008290_ALISAIE<tab>[SOBBING] Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008290_ALISAIE<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008300_ALISAIE<tab>You can't leave us... Not like this...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008300_ALISAIE<tab>(-???-)Ouvre les yeux... Tu peux pas nous faire ça...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008310_ALISAIE<tab>If you do, I'll never forgive you... So, come on! Open your eyes and get up!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008310_ALISAIE<tab>(-???-)Tu nous as même pas dit au revoir...<var 1D /var>! Je te le pardonnerai jamais si tu nous quittes maintenant<var 1D /var>! Alors, réveille-toi<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008320_ALISAIE<tab>[GASP] Report if displayed
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008320_ALISAIE<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008330_ALPHINAUD<tab>Are you...are you with us?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008330_ALPHINAUD<tab>Tu es de retour avec nous, ça y est<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008340_ALPHINAUD<tab>Thank the heavens... For a moment we thought...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008340_ALPHINAUD<tab> Merci... Merci...<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q15_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_Q15_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que dites-vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A15_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Is everyone all right?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A15_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Personne n'est blessé<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A15_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Am I really alive?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_A15_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Est-ce que je suis au paradis<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008350_GRAHATIA<tab>After what you've done, you're the last person...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008350_GRAHATIA<tab>Tout le monde va bien... Mais toi...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008360_GRAHATIA<tab>...To be asking that.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008360_GRAHATIA<tab>Toi... tu nous en as fait une belle...<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008370_GRAHATIA<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008370_GRAHATIA<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008380_GRAHATIA<tab>Yes, you're alive.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008380_GRAHATIA<tab>Rassure-toi. Tu es toujourrrs...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008390_GRAHATIA<tab>You're alive...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008390_GRAHATIA<tab>Parrrmi les vivants...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008400_GRAHATIA<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008400_GRAHATIA<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008410_GRAHATIA<tab>You... How can you keep your promise if you're not here?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008410_GRAHATIA<tab>Qu'est-ce que je ferais... si t'étais plus là pour tenir notre prrromesse, hein<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008420_ESTINIEN<tab>Another fine show you've put on, my friend.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008420_ESTINIEN<tab>Salut, camarade. Tu as encore fait feu de tout bois, dis-moi<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008430_YSHTOLA<tab>A fine show indeed...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008430_YSHTOLA<tab>Je suis heureuse que tu t'en sois sorti<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> indemne.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008440_YSHTOLA<tab>What were you thinking, fighting alone? Never do that again. My poor heart couldn't bear it.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008440_YSHTOLA<tab>Mais soyons bien clairs<var 1D /var>: c'est la dernière fois que tu te bats sans nous. Tu as idée du sang d'encre qu'on s'est fait, au moins<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008450_THANCRED<tab>Put yourself in our place. If you hadn't returned, how do you think we would feel? And if that sounds harsh...it's because we care.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008450_THANCRED<tab>Y'shtola a raison. Imagine un peu, que serions-nous devenus si tu n'étais jamais revenu<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var><var 1D /var>? Mets-toi à notre place, pour une fois...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008460_URIANGER<tab>We tended to thy wounds as best we could, but how is the pain?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008460_URIANGER<tab>Nous vous avons soigné<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> du mieux que nous pouvions. Est-ce que ça va aller<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008470_URIANGER<tab>That is gladdening. Grievous as thine injuries were, however, I would counsel repose for a time.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008470_URIANGER<tab>J'en suis ravi... Toutefois, vous avez subi de profondes blessures, alors ménagez-vous, s'il vous plaît.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008480_ALISAIE<tab>Gladdening!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008480_ALISAIE<tab>Je suis pas ravie du tout, moi<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008490_ALISAIE<tab>There's nothing gladdening about this!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008490_ALISAIE<tab>Mais alors, vraiment pas du tout<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008500_ALISAIE<tab>When Meteion appeared in here and told us that you were right behind her, we all got our hopes up. But you never came!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008500_ALISAIE<tab>Météion est passée nous dire que t'étais pas loin derrière... On a attendu gentiment... sans se douter que t'aurais le culot de jouer les retardataires<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008510_ALISAIE<tab>And when you finally deign to appear, you're within an ilm of your life!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008510_ALISAIE<tab>Et quand tu te décides enfin à arriver, tu débarques à moitié mort<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> au milieu de la pièce<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008520_ALISAIE<tab>Damn you! Damn you for making us worry!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008520_ALISAIE<tab>Imbécile<var 1D /var>! J'ai cru qu'on allait jamais te revoir<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008530_LIVINGWAY<tab>Ah, those were cries of celebration.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008530_LIVINGWAY<tab>Alors <var 08 E905 ((elle)) ((il)) /var> va bien<var 1D /var>!? Heureuse de voir notre équipage au complet<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008540_LIVINGWAY<tab>Anyway, what the important thing is that you're all alive and in reasonably good health, and we mean to get you back that way.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008540_LIVINGWAY<tab>Nous allons manœuvrer prudemment et éviter de trop vous secouer. Profitez-en pour vous reposer.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008550_LIVINGWAY<tab>As for your earlier request, I'm quite certain we're in range to make contact now.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008550_LIVINGWAY<tab>En ce qui concerne votre requête, nous devrions maintenant être à portée de communication.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008560_THANCRED<tab>Ah, excellent. Let us announce our return at once.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008560_THANCRED<tab>Ah, ça tombe bien, je n'ai plus que des bonnes nouvelles à annoncer à l'Alliance.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008570_THANCRED<tab>I hope you're ready.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008570_THANCRED<tab>L'accueil sera triomphal, alors j'espère que tu tiendras debout.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008580_ALPHINAUD<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008580_ALPHINAUD<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008590_ALPHINAUD<tab>While you were unconscious, we set out from Ultima Thule, you see.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008590_ALPHINAUD<tab>Nous sommes partis d'Ultima Thulé et avons pris le chemin du retour pendant que tu étais sans con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>san<var 16 /var>ce.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008600_ALPHINAUD<tab>Can you stand? If so, you may wish to see what's outside.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008600_ALPHINAUD<tab>Tu penses pouvoir te lever<var 1D /var>? À mon avis, tu ne voudras pas rater le spectacle.
