source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008610_ALPHINAUD<tab>We're home, my friend. We're home!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008610_ALPHINAUD<tab>Nous sommes de retour chez nous, regarde comme notre planète est belle<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008620_ERENVILLE<tab>Is that...?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008620_ERENVILLE<tab>Là-bas...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008630_ERENVILLE<tab>It is! It's the <var 1A 02 /var>Ragnarok<var 1A 01 /var>! They're back!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008630_ERENVILLE<tab>C'est lui, c'est le Ragnarok. Ils sont de retour<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008640_WILFSUNN<tab>Thank heavens...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008640_WILFSUNN<tab>Le destin soit remercié...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008650_BLOEWYDA<tab>Truly.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008650_BLOEWYDA<tab>Plutôt deux fois qu'une.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008660_SICARD<tab>Yes!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008660_SICARD<tab>Hourra<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008670_EMMANELLAIN<tab>They've done it!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008670_EMMANELLAIN<tab>Hourra<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008680_SOROBAN<tab>Welcome home!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008680_SOROBAN<tab>Les revoilàààà<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008690_HOARYBOULDER<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008690_HOARYBOULDER<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008700_CID<tab>Yes!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008700_CID<tab>Ouais<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008710_FOURCHENAULT<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008710_FOURCHENAULT<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008720_KRILE<tab>
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008720_KRILE<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008730_TATARU<tab>Welcome home, everyone!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008730_TATARU<tab>Vous voilà<var 1D /var>! Enfin de retour<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008740_TATARU<tab>Welcome home!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008740_TATARU<tab>Bienvenue chez vous<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008750_ALPHINAUD<tab>Dearest Mother, Dearest Father...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008750_ALPHINAUD<tab>Chère Maman, cher Papa,

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008760_ALPHINAUD<tab>This letter will be the very last that I write to you from the Rising Stones.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008760_ALPHINAUD<tab>Cette lettre est pro<var 16 /var>ba<var 16 /var>ble<var 16 /var>ment la dernière que je vous écris depuis le Refuge des roches.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008770_ALPHINAUD<tab>As I commit these words to parchment, I fondly recall my journey as a Scion.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008770_ALPHINAUD<tab>Chaque trait de ma plume évoque aujourd'hui en moi un souvenir de mon temps passé ici, au sein des Héritiers.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008780_ALPHINAUD<tab>From the time I first walked into the order's former halls...to the time I set forth to forestall the Final Days.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008780_ALPHINAUD<tab>De notre arrivée dans le Mor Dhona. Jusqu'à notre grand départ pour repousser l'apocalypse qui menaçait notre monde.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008790_ALPHINAUD<tab>At the farthest reaches of the sea of stars, we fought the battle of our lives...
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008790_ALPHINAUD<tab>Notre ultime combat nous aura menés bien au-delà de nos cieux si familiers.
Pourtant, ces distances astronomiques me paraissent bien peu de choses.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008800_ALPHINAUD<tab>Fought against despair itself─a veritable maelstrom of it fed by the resignation that dwelled in the hearts of beings not so unlike ourselves.
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008800_ALPHINAUD<tab>Car à tout prendre, n'est-ce pas à portée de cœur que nous avons comblé l'abîme de désespoir auquel nous faisions face<var 1D /var>?
Plus j'y pense et plus j'en ai la conviction.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008810_ALPHINAUD<tab>Full oft have I harbored the same malaise. Have I been brought to my knees, crushed by the weight of sorrow and defeat, convinced that I will never rise again.
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008810_ALPHINAUD<tab>Pour être tout à fait honnête, j'ai moi-même contemplé cet abîme à maintes et maintes reprises,
et j'ai failli me noyer plus d'une fois dans ses tourbillons de tristesse et de regrets.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008820_ALPHINAUD<tab>However...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008820_ALPHINAUD<tab>Toutefois,

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008830_ALPHINAUD<tab>I have also known many moments of unbridled joy and happiness.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008830_ALPHINAUD<tab>j'ai toujours pu jeter un regard en arrière, et me rappeler les jours heureux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008840_ALPHINAUD<tab>By this truth do I find hope within, blooming resplendent like the Elpis flower.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008840_ALPHINAUD<tab>À l'instar de cette fleur, synonyme d'espoir, ces précieux souvenirs ont toujours su me redonner courage.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008850_ALPHINAUD<tab>And thus do I endure.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008850_ALPHINAUD<tab>Voilà pourquoi,

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008860_ALPHINAUD<tab>Do I look forward to creating more memories with my friends and loved ones.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008860_ALPHINAUD<tab>je veux continuer à rire avec mes amis d'aujourd'hui, et avec ceux de demain.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008865_ALPHINAUD<tab>For from these fertile seeds, yet more hope shall spring forth...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008865_ALPHINAUD<tab>Pour semer de nouvelles graines qui germeront un jour, et peut-être...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008870_ALPHINAUD<tab>And they will grow to become shining lights that illuminate the dark.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008870_ALPHINAUD<tab>rallumer le flambeau de l'espoir, dans les abîmes les plus sombres.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008880_ALPHINAUD<tab>Thus believing, I leave the Rising Stones behind, as will my comrades.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008880_ALPHINAUD<tab>C'est avec ce vœu au fond de mon cœur que je m'apprête à quitter notre refuge.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008890_ALPHINAUD<tab>For as we have decided after careful deliberation...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008890_ALPHINAUD<tab>Les autres et moi en avons longuement discuté, et avons enfin pris notre décision<var 1D /var>:

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008900_ALPHINAUD<tab>We are disbanding the Scions of the Seventh Dawn.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008900_ALPHINAUD<tab>les Héritiers de la Septième Aube... se séparent.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008910_TATARU<tab>There you are, Alphinaud!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008910_TATARU<tab>Ah<var 1D /var>! Alphinaud<var 1D /var>! Vous étiez encore là<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008920_TATARU<tab>Everyone is already gathered in the foyer!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008920_TATARU<tab>Dépêchez-vous, vous êtes le dernier<var 1D /var>! Tout le monde vous attend<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008930_ALPHINAUD<tab>My apologies. I'll be right there.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008930_ALPHINAUD<tab>Déjà<var 1D /var>? Désolé, j'arrive dans un instant.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008940_ALPHINAUD<tab>At least...that is what the story will be.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008940_ALPHINAUD<tab>Officiellement, tout du moins.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008950_ALPHINAUD<tab>Sorry to keep you all waiting.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008950_ALPHINAUD<tab>Désolé de vous avoir fait attendre.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008960_ALISAIE<tab>What could you possibly have left to do now?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008960_ALISAIE<tab>Qu'est-ce que tu faisais<var 1D /var>? C'est le grand jour.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008970_ALPHINAUD<tab>Oh, just a letter.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008970_ALPHINAUD<tab>J'écrivais une lettre pour qui tu sais.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008980_THANCRED<tab>I imagine it will be a while before we can gather like this again.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008980_THANCRED<tab>On ne se reverra pas tous ensemble comme ça avant un moment.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008990_YSHTOLA<tab>So it must be if we're to keep up appearances.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_008990_YSHTOLA<tab>Les Héritiers de la Septième Aube sont dissous. À compter d'aujourd'hui, ce sont des or<var 16 /var>ga<var 16 /var>ni<var 16 /var>sa<var 16 /var>tions comme la Grande compagnie éorzéenne qui s'attelleront à la résolution des problèmes géopolitiques.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009000_YSHTOLA<tab>From now on, it falls to the Grand Company of Eorzea and its allies to deal with the realm's crises.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009000_YSHTOLA<tab>Le simple fait de nous réunir irait à l'encontre de ce que nous avons annoncé. Alors autant s'y tenir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009010_URIANGER<tab>Meanwhile, we shall return to our erstwhile ways.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009010_URIANGER<tab>Et puis, il s'agira davantage d'un retour aux sources pour nous.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009020_URIANGER<tab>Retreating from plain sight to take our place in the shadows once more.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009020_URIANGER<tab>Après tout, Minfilia avait créé une société secrète. Nous ne ferons donc que perpétuer cet héritage.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009030_ALPHINAUD<tab>Indeed. For the foreseeable future, I expect that we must work independently as we seek out problems that want for solving.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009030_ALPHINAUD<tab>C'est bien vrai. Et n'oublions pas que chacun d'entre nous parcourra désormais le monde pour apporter son aide là où elle est requise.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009040_ALPHINAUD<tab>But a day will come when we face another great challenge. And we will face it together, as we always have.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009040_ALPHINAUD<tab>Nul doute que quelqu'un finira par se retrouver face à une menace de taille. D'ici là, nous aurons encore plus mûri, et nous nous retrouverons pour affronter ensemble ce péril.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009050_KRILE<tab>As much as I look forward to that day, I do hope it doesn't come any time soon...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009050_KRILE<tab>Hmm... Faut-il prier pour que ce jour arrive vite ou non, là est la question...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009060_ESTINIEN<tab>Well, formal association or no, if any of you should require my services, you need but ask.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009060_ESTINIEN<tab>Bah, vous savez ce que j'en pense des réunions en grande pompe. Si l'un d'entre vous a besoin d'un coup de main, vous m'appelez, c'est tout.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009070_ESTINIEN<tab>I'll be glad to keep my lance arm honed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009070_ESTINIEN<tab>Et n'allez pas croire que ma lance prendra la rouille en attendant.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009080_THANCRED<tab>I'll hold you to that, so you had better keep your linkpearl on hand.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009080_THANCRED<tab>C'est pas tombé dans l'oreille d'un sourd. Prends soin de la linkperle que je t'ai filée, d'accord<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009090_ALISAIE<tab>So, you really mean to stay, Tataru?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009090_ALISAIE<tab>Tu as dit que tu restais ici toi, Tataru, c'est ça<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009100_TATARU<tab>Someone has to keep the Rising Stones in proper order, and even a super-secret organization requires a super-secret base of operations.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009100_TATARU<tab>Tout à fait<var 1D /var>! Société secrète ou pas, il vous faut un point de chute. Et pas envahi par la poussière et les toiles d'araignée, de préférence.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009110_TATARU<tab>To the rest of the world, it will be naught more than a workshop for Eorzea's foremost up-and-coming artisan!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009110_TATARU<tab>Le Refuge des roches sera donc reconverti en atelier<var 1D /var>! Celui de Tataru, artisane émérite<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009120_TATARU<tab>If you thought our coffers were full to bursting before, just wait till I can devote myself wholly to the crafts.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009120_TATARU<tab>Je vais en brasser des millions, c'est moi qui vous le dis<var 1D /var>! Même des milliards, qui sait<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009130_ALISAIE<tab>Plotting to build a mercantile empire to rival that of Lord Lolorito, are we?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009130_ALISAIE<tab>C'est qu'on nous mettrait presque à la porte.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009135_GRAHATIA<tab>[LAUGHS] Report if displayed.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009135_GRAHATIA<tab>

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009140_GRAHATIA<tab>I, for one, look forward to your future successes, Tataru, as do I our next meeting.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009140_GRAHATIA<tab>Ce ne sera pas pour tout de suite, mais j'attendrai avec impatience le jourrr de nos retrouvailles.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009150_TATARU<tab>And with that, I believe it is past time you all made ready to depart.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009150_TATARU<tab>Bien<var 1D /var>! Je vais vous laisser terminer vos préparatifs<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009160_TATARU<tab>Leave no preparations undone or words unsaid, all right? Now, off with you!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009160_TATARU<tab>Nous ne nous reverrons pas avant un moment, alors pensez à tous vous dire au revoir<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009170_ALISAIE<tab>I suppose we're off to Garlemald, then.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009170_ALISAIE<tab>Bon ben... Alphinaud et moi, on va se mettre en route pour Ishgard.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009180_ALISAIE<tab>Though we ought to speak with Lord Aymeric first. If he's received word of any recent developments, we need to know.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009180_ALISAIE<tab>Sire Aymeric reçoit en permanence les derniers rapports de la délégation d'Ilsabard, il devrait pouvoir nous renseigner sur la situation à Garlemald.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009190_ALPHINAUD<tab>'Twould be prudent to purchase some warmer clothes at least. Mayhap we can pick up a few souvenirs for Jullus and the others while we're at it.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009190_ALPHINAUD<tab>Au fait, comme on doit faire le tour du marché pour se trouver une petite laine, si on achetait quelques souvenirs pour Jullus et les autres<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009200_ALISAIE<tab>Where will you all be heading next?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009200_ALISAIE<tab>Et vous<var 1D /var>? Quoi de prévu<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009210_YSHTOLA<tab>Dravania. There is a book I have been meaning to borrow from the Great Gubal Library.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009210_YSHTOLA<tab>Per<var 16 /var>son<var 16 /var>nel<var 16 /var>le<var 16 /var>ment, je dois faire un petit tour dans l'Arrière-pays dravanien. Je cherche un livre, et il a de grandes chances d'être en train de prendre la poussière sur une étagère dans la Grande bibliothèque de Gubal.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009220_YSHTOLA<tab>And I can think of at least one person who will be most displeased should I fail to visit before leaving.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009220_YSHTOLA<tab>J'en profiterai aussi pour passer dire bonjour à la plus grande tête de mule de la région.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009230_THANCRED<tab>We've no particular destination in mind, but we do intend to stop in Sharlayan before we set off.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009230_THANCRED<tab>En ce qui nous concerne, on sait pas trop encore. Mais on va commencer par se rendre à Sharlayan.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009240_URIANGER<tab>We had thought to ask after the Loporrits. I am curious as to how well those who chose to remain are adapting to their changed circumstances.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009240_URIANGER<tab>En fait, certains Loporrites sont restés ici, et je suis curieux de connaitre leurs projets.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009250_KRILE<tab>Might we accompany you, then? Raha and I were planning to return to the Baldesion Annex.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009250_KRILE<tab>À ce compte-là, faisons un bout de route ensemble. Nous devons retourner à l'annexe des Élèves de Baldesion.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009260_GRAHATIA<tab>Commissions have been piling up in our absence, and they must be dealt with ere we begin our work in earnest.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009260_GRAHATIA<tab>Il parrraît que les demandes d'enquête n'ont pas cessé de s'empiler der<var 16 /var>niè<var 16 /var>re<var 16 /var>ment. On va commencer pas faire le tri là-dedans.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009270_ALPHINAUD<tab>Estinien. You will return to Radz-at-Han, will you not?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009270_ALPHINAUD<tab>C'est destination Radz-at-Han pour toi, Estinien, c'est ça<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009280_ESTINIEN<tab>Aye. For Vrtra's benefit, though I've yet to hear the details. I may not stay long.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009280_ESTINIEN<tab>Oui... Je n'y prendrai peut-être pas racine, mais je dois au moins écouter ce que Vrtra a à me dire.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009290_ALPHINAUD<tab>I see. Then it is here the Scions at last part ways, each to some far-flung corner of the realm.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009290_ALPHINAUD<tab>Nous partons tous dans des directions différentes... C'est donc ici qu'on se dit au revoir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009300_YSHTOLA<tab>Perhaps. But I believe one of our number─a rather important one, at that─has yet to divulge <var 08 E905 ((her)) ((his)) /var> plans.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009300_YSHTOLA<tab>On va y venir, mais avant ça, j'en connais un<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> qui n'a pas encore répondu à la question.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009310_ESTINIEN<tab>Quite right.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009310_ESTINIEN<tab>Alors, camarade<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009320_URIANGER<tab>Indeed...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009320_URIANGER<tab>Dites-nous tout.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009330_GRAHATIA<tab>Fair point!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009330_GRAHATIA<tab>On veut savoirrr<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009340_ALPHINAUD<tab>So. What's next for our humble adventurer?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009340_ALPHINAUD<tab>Et toi<var 1D /var>? Quelle sera ta prochaine aventure<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009350_ELIDIBUS<tab>(-???-)The constancy of this place never ceases to amaze me. An ocean of souls, shimmering and eternal.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009350_ELIDIBUS<tab>(-???-)Le spectacle offert par ces îlots flottant dans le ciel est toujours aussi saisissant. La vie dans toute sa majesté luxuriante et persistante.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009360_ELIDIBUS<tab>(-???-)And yet...something stirs...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009360_ELIDIBUS<tab>(-???-)Pourtant, je le sens... Quelque chose grouille dans les tréfonds de la terre...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009370_ELIDIBUS<tab>(-???-)Yes... Steeped in darkness deep as starless night, the beast hungers.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009370_ELIDIBUS<tab>(-???-)Dans l'ombre, là où nulle lumière céleste ne saurait pénétrer, des myriades de créatures maléfiques s'agitent...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009380_ELIDIBUS<tab>(-???-)Alas, I dare not investigate in earnest before the coming of my guiding star, as he foretold.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009380_ELIDIBUS<tab>(-???-)Qu'il me tarde de déterminer la source de ce tumulte... Mais attendons l'arrivée de cet “astre” dont tu as prédit la venue, mon ami.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009390_ELIDIBUS<tab>(-???-)Alas, I dare not investigate in earnest before the coming of my guiding star, as she foretold.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009390_ELIDIBUS<tab>(-???-)Qu'il me tarde de déterminer la source de ce tumulte... Mais attendons la venue de cet “astre”, comme tu me l'as conseillé, mon amie.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009400_ELIDIBUS<tab>(-???-)We shall descend to the depths, you and I, to confront the dread beast Pandæmonium.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009400_ELIDIBUS<tab>(-???-)Reste à savoir de quel astre tu parlais. Qui pourrait bien m'accompagner dans le Pandæmonium pour faire la lumière sur ses mystères...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009410_ELIDIBUS<tab>(-???-)Oh, the sights we shall see. The sights we shall see.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06006_009410_ELIDIBUS<tab>(-???-)Qui que tu sois, j'ai hâte que nous fassions con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>san<var 16 /var>ce, toi et moi.
